('129115403803409_10152054817153371', 'Parking is being collected in Alipore Road, the lane in which Woodlands Hospital Located.\nVehicles are made to park on the pavement meant for pedestrians.\n So called parking attendants claim that they have permission from KMC.\nWonder, since when KMC started issuing permission for parking on pavement?\n Fee Parking Boards are missing\n Parking Attendants ID Card a miss\nthe picture shows the license got expired on 2013 but they are still collecting parking.\nCalled up 9830010000 on 24th February 2014 at 6.18pm complaining about the same, got a response we don\'t have this information, we may complain with KMC.\nHome Guard on duty was witness to the situation but didn\'t intervene.\nAn ASI came to the scene but did not involve himself\nSeems like the local PS or Traffic Guard have information about the Parking Scandal going on there.\n\nPlease do rectify me, if i am mistaken.', '2014-02-25T18:16:32+0000', 'negative'),
