('129115403803409_10152112071596218', 'Sir, I hv always patronized Kolkata Police & their commendable efforts in putting system in place. But today I felt extremely let down. I walked down to DL Khan Road Shib Mandir crossing all the way from exide being refused by every taxi driver to take me to Calcutta Hospital. I saw an individual white uniform (picture)taking a nap and one in blue perched on a bike (picture of the bike). I walked up to them seeking help. Not only they humiliated me in front of other by standers..they made fun of me..challenged me saying I could do nothing to them..n this is why they let me click pictures too. I asked them for their names they said Debu and abdul rakhib...dunno how genuine these names are..so I clicked a pic of their bike..I felt bullied..all the taxis..abt 8 of them parked by the Nuero science hospital and 3 taxis parked beside the guru tegh bahadur hospital refused to take me to CMRI. I pleaded telling them I was fasting n their was no other way of reaching my house from there quickly as time for iftar was running away...all in vain..Thanks to this mocking gentleman. .\n\nI dont know what would become of this complaint but I really hope to see thru this..\n\nPLEASE HELP!!!', '2014-07-07T13:49:53+0000', 'negative'),
