('129115403803409_10152602754029983', 'I had asked this taxi to go to Hindustan International Hotel.This is taxi photo with driver. This is a No Refusal Cab. But refusing by saying that the taxi is reserved. Though no passenger is there in the taxi.  Place is near Pathbhavan senior section school. Bondel Road. Not only this taxi but most of the empty taxis plying on the road is straightway refusing to go. Also he is not wearing uniform while driving the taxi.', '2014-11-23T12:49:35+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10152618639880236', 'This incident happened at 8.45am today the 31st august at the Simultala/ Blind School Taxi Stand. I along with my parents came to the taxi stand by 2 cycle rickshas and asked the driver to take us to St Thomas\' School Kidderpore.  We had a foldable wheelchair with us. We were straight away told that he would charge rs. 30 extra as charges for carrying the foldable wheelchair in the dickie or luggage compartment of the cab and then refused saying that he won\'t take us if we don\'t pay. I asked the driver as well as the stand in charge what kind of a rule was that and he said he didn\'t care we had to pay. I\'m sending his license plate number here and it is my humble request to take strict action against this person who disrespected my 78 year old father and refused to take a person on a wheelchair AND demanded an extra fee for carrying it. Also please enlighten me if there are any such rules about paying a fee for wheelchair carrying for an invalid person. If there is I will be more than glad to comply by the rule.', '2014-08-31T07:05:22+0000', 'positive'),
