('129115403803409_10152711415965812', 'Taxi refusal complaint against the driver of the taxi whose pic is enclosed. Concern 1: Does a taxi driver with a \'No refusal\' printed taxi, have the right to refuse picking up the customer? Concern 2: Why should a taxi driver refuse a taxi after hearing the destination? In fact, if he is resting/ waiting for any other customer, why should he even bother to ask the destination? Concern 3: Why does a driver ask for additional fare over and above the actual?\nThis is an everyday scenario faced by thousands of customers. No wonder private cab services are gaining popularity! Why isn\'t the Government taking any action?', '2015-04-09T04:38:52+0000', 'negative'),
