('129115403803409_10153385963843565', 'With due respect I,Sudip Mondal do want to draw your kind attention regarding an important issue & some others too which I & many people have been facing recently by any means.\n\nDay Before Yesterday[03-12-2015] evening I have received a letter from Kolkata Traffic Police (On Government of India Service) sent on 28-11-2015 stating that I/my vehicle have violated 301WBMVR/177MVA(U/S Code) with the Offence of \'Pedestrial Line Violation\' on Dated 17-11-2015 at 11:12 AM with Stated Case No. - aaTW038849/15 to my Vehicle No. - WB01AE6777 at Rabindra Sarani/India Exchange Place/Cit Road.\n\nNow I do want to state that I was in my home the whole day along with my vehicle (on which the case had been generated) on that day. (Specially I remember the day for the event of Kartik Puja & Chhat Puja together this year) Even I have proof & witnesses to justify my statement such as My mobile tower locations & access, Family Members & Others, even I don\'t & didn\'t allowed any one else to drive my vehicle ever & also on that day too as usual & I posses both the given keys with me & in safe custody always when unused & moreover my vehicle is equipped with anti lock system pre-installed which clearly states that it cannot be started without this two keys in this world except manufacturer makes any dublicate which is subject to my authorization, I along with my vehicle has never been to the mentioned place in my life & specially on the given date & time (which can be further scrutinized by means of CCTV installed in the surroundings & each exit points of that place of offence occurrence which recorded all events on road on that day more over Your Head Quarter also lies in that Locality as well as scrutinizing whole Kolkata\'s Installed CCTV would be more better).etc.\n\nNow understanding this issue I came to the following conclusions that after thinking all the possibilities for one whole day-\n\n1. Either there is any other vehicle/s using my number which is responsible for the offence which really is a nightmare for anyone facing it as well as me & really an important thing to worry about at present situations which is prevailing throughout the world.\n\n2. Or may be the person responsible for placing the case have serious distant visionary issues who cannot detect the difference between \'6111\' (perhaps) & \'6777\' because both  the numbers are illusive & non-identical which resembles more or less if seen from a certain distance during day or night for some one having distant vision-problem. As it is stated clearly that the vehicle was violating Pedestrial Line that means the vehicle was obeying the signal (if any) & obstructing the pedestrian\'s lane being static on the road which could have been stopped right at that place & could have been penalised with Spot Fine which clearly proves that the person placing the case was not near to the place of occurrence of the offence on the given particular day & time. Thats why he/she had to generate the case remotely or online in this manner due to distance or any other protocol/s obeyed if any.\n\n3. Or quote un quote there must be any Fresher/Newly recruited who was supposed to reach his/her Target given by the person\'s Senior on duty who anonymously imposed case against my Vehicle number illegally with out thinking of anything else.(I heard this kind of things often from General Public as well as some Police Officers too even possessing High Ranks & Posts in your Department. Although its a mystery to me & needs to be scrutinized further. Kindly don\'t take it as a obvious statement & I don\'t want to disclose or render anyone\'s name in this regard.\n\n4. Or I am lying completely.\n\n5. Or any other further reasons which may be unknown to me & needs to be detected yet.\n\nI as a citizen of India humbly request You & Your Department or any other responsible authorised personnel to look into the mater immediately with full concern & to resolve & conclude the raised issue with a fruitful result at an early date.\n\nI appeal to the core of your heart to response me [with an answer at least (which may be in my against)] but can satisfy my querry to the aforesaid Contact Details.\n\n***As its second time I have been sent a letter from your Department despite of My or My Vehicle\'s involvement in any Offence Violating any Law.\n\n(I paid the Previous Fine of Rs. 100/= as suggested by An O.C. previously whom I personally know & I discussed the mater with him for the \nCase no.- ooTW006032/15 \nDated - 16-01-2015 \nTime - 19-21 \nPlace - In front of Gems Cinema on A.J.C. Bose Road/Jems Cinema\nOffence - Without Helmet\nU/S Code : 129/177 MVA\n\nWhich I didn\'t commited as that Day too, I was in my home the whole day along with my vehicle in which the case had been generated as it was One year Completition of my Mothers Death & We all were performing Hindu rituals for her Souls Peace with Family Members & Guests who were with me the whole day even some in night too & I or any co-passenger travelling with me always wear IS 4151 specified Helmets every time while travelling or on journey to one place to another.). Thats why he told to pay the fine instead of raising any voice.\n\nBut this time I am really shocked & worried so discussing the mater or a Habitudal Truth very frankly with you.\n\nWe the Citizens are very much dependent on your Kind Service which your Department renders 24/7 to us.Your Department is famous for Transperancy & Dedication through out the Globe.Our trust will always be with you & Our Constitution . Perhaps You too will co-operate us solving every problem in future too.\n\nMY KIND SUGGESTION : \n\n1. Install High Definition Automated CCTV Programable Cameras at proper places with intervals which can record any event occured in any where which can accompany the case letters with evidences too.As Used in Bangaluru,Delhi & many other places in the world.\n\n2. Recommend A Unique Electromagnetic Identifying Device at Signals or Crossings as well as Identifiers to each Registered Vehicle (Old/New) or (Free GPS Networks & Devices in Vehicles or in the Driver\'s/Owner\'s or Authorised Driver\'s Smart Phone with a unique password to connect travelling in a particular vehicle which should be mandatory to keep on while driving & to show to authorised persons if asked in any place along with other documents) which can state the Presence & Position of any vehicle at any given time & date in the country.\n\nMy earnest request kindly take this issue as a friend not as a Police Personal so that in future you can eradicate any Public Harasment & also spending your valuable time reading this kind of issues as stated by me with due respect to your department & all in person. I condemn if I hurted anyone by any means in my aforesaid statement/s & also praying for forgiving me in advance if so.\n\nSudip Mondal.\nHouse No- 57/1 S.R.Das Road [Mudiali Club Area] P.S. - Tollygunge. P.O. - Kalighat.\nWard No - 87. Kolkata - 700 026. West Bengal.\nContact Numbers - +91-9831082439 , +91-8820456199 , +91-9062428599.', '2015-12-04T21:54:34+0000', 'positive'),
