('129115403803409_10154273275748007', 'Dear Kolkata traffic police\nWednesday,15th june 2016, below coal india building, netaji subhash road Kolkata 700001 11:30 am.\nWe found A person was using his car key and was deflating  the tyre of my car claiming  that the parking slot belongs to him and he will keep on doing the same with everybody whoever parks their car in that slot. While  started recording the video and protesting the act, the situation went out of control and that person fled inside coal india building . The watchman restricted us to enter the premises though he protected him and  allowed  him to enter the premises. Thus it is clear either he is a coal india employee or a known person to the watchman. When we asked his name they denied to tell us the name .  On calling lalbazar control room 2 officers from hare street police station  managed to reach the spot after 20 mins. Officer on the spot advised us to file a GD in hare street police station . while filing the GD we were  told to come between 3:00 – 3:30 pm with the recording and a picture of him. As told we reached the police station at 3:00pm but was surprised when  they refused to take the GD on the ground that we don’t know his name. On several request he took the GD after some alteration. GD was taken in unknown name and till now we are not aware of any action taken against the said person', '2016-06-16T12:44:30+0000', 'neutral'),
