('129115403803409_10154639701673756', 'This is a picture from today, in follow up to my complaint on 19th October, 2016. \n\nAs you see, after Puja\'s, it back to illegality as usual. \n\nThe second light post has a nice little \"No Parking for Goods Vehicles\" sign, which is ignored by truckers & police alike. Again less that 50m from New Alipore Police Station. \n\nIllegal activities allowed for trucks, bike gangs, autos & cycle-thelas but only private car owners are prosecuted everywhere?\n\nWhat follow up after my original complaint? Nothing.\n\nWhy not go and patrol this stretch and clamp illegal trucks? Is it because of apathy to citizens? Or something else?\n\nMukund Chamria 9836389892 lets see if you do something this time.', '2016-10-29T06:02:24+0000', 'neutral'),
