('129115403803409_10154827067831885', 'This is a picture of a sergeant on a bike having registration number  WB01A G4288. The picture suggests 2 violations for sure. One he is on the wrong side of camac street and secondly he is chitchatting with his known people in the middle of the road. I was in view of the entire episode and the sergeant was standing in the middle of the road for more than 15 minutes chit chatting with his known people. I am sorry to say but people who are suppose to enforce law if the blatantly break the same it is painful. All the vehicles getting in from Park street to enter camac street had to negotiate the sergeant sitting on his bike middle of the road and that too for more than 15 minutes. I am not interested in your department penalizing the sergeant but I am interested that you call the sergeant and just show him this photograph and ask him as to what was he doing in the middle of the road in peak traffic hours. \nPic taken on 14.2.17 @ 5 pm', '2017-02-15T09:22:23+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10154846780596896', 'Dear Kolkata Police, please can you help !!!\n\nThe backside of Uma Medical, Teghoria VIP road has been turned into illegal parking spot. The residents now only have 4-5 feet road left. We are a community of more than 500 with 100+ cars crossing this stretch on a daily basis. This is becoming a serious threat for daily commute as well as for emergency services.  @bidhannagar traffic police for info as you have a traffic guard just 100 ft away ..', '2017-06-04T04:40:06+0000', 'negative'),
