('129115403803409_10154877488521030', 'Seeking Attention...!!\n\nI am not sure if a Govt/public servant is allowed to use such language on duty.. the behaviour of the police official is not expected from Kolkata traffic police.. \nIn the recorded video, the person against whom the cases were filed, asked the official to explain the guilty and the charges, Two police person said two different reasons. And in stead of traffic police station or court, the official is quoting (read Threatening) to see this guy in High court.\n\n\"I will see you there\", is a kind of terminology used by the goons.. Not expected from Kolkata traffic police.. \n\nIn another way, this kind of statement depicts like High court is his ancestral property.. \n\nSorry to say, this is not the culture of bengal or Kolkata that we would like to see growing from its present.. \n\nMoloy Ghatak - Kaku.. Sorkar o Tar Kormochari der gothonmulok kaajer prosongsha jemon hoy.. Sangothonik o Proshashonik Kaaj e jukto sorkari kormochari der (Bisheshoto jara jonogoner songe protyokkho byaboharik kaaj e nijukto) kichuta holeo sohonsheelota o bhodrota r proshikkhon o dewa hok.. Notuba ei dhoroner durbyabohar ebong du-sprodha aro berei cholbe..\n\n', '2016-08-24T16:34:22+0000', 'positive'),
