('129115403803409_10155062153303988', 'Face Detection and Recognition has immense power. It can be used in various use cases. One of such  use case can be Criminal Identification.\nInvestigation agencies can obtain picture of criminal/ terrorists from different sources like Drawing sketch from eye witness and Picture from CC TV footage.\nThe problem lies to find out the whereabouts of such criminals if they do not poses any previous criminal records. It has been noticed that investigation agencies take some time to find out the whereabouts of such criminal or they are not able to trace them at all. As a result criminal cases remains unsolved.\nIBM Lab has come up with a face recognition API, which is still under development stage. With this API two faces can be compared, based on the comparison it would return match score. I have built a POC which crawls different FB Profiles and compare it with the input image with the help of IBM Face detection API. Based on the match score it shows different profile which are the nearest matches with the Criminal image.\nhttps://www.slideshare.net/amitavar/trace-criminal-using-ibm-watson\n\nIf you feel interesting kindly contact me.', '2017-02-23T06:24:54+0000', 'positive'),
