('129115403803409_10156327939760290', 'Hello,\n\nGreetings from Gems B School, Bengaluru.\n\nA few years back we started a social initiative with the purpose of spreading the message \"DO NOT DRINK AND DRIVE ON NEW YEAR\'S EVE\" and ever since then every year we are been spreading this message effectively through various mediums. \n\nThis year we have created a short film /video to spread the awareness to the general public and this video has gone viral on the social media with over 1 lakh views in less than 48 hours.\n\nHere is the face book link to this video \nhttps://www.facebook.com/GEMSBSchool/videos/1059301860776429/\n\nWe would urge you to share this on your face book page as the response of the public to this video has been overwhelming. I am sure your followers on facebook would appreciate our effort towards this cause.\n\nWe would also be glad to share a copy of this video with you if you would like to telecast it on some other medium. \n\nThanks\n\nBest Wishes\n\nKunal Nehruji', '2015-12-30T07:23:36+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10156413029715556', 'A No Refusal Yellow Taxi (WB04E1980) rudely refused to take us from Kasba to Ballygunj on 25th October 2015 at around 8:30pm. The driver claimed that there was an enormous jam on the road. We started to walk, but thankfully got a different taxi later. There was no jam on the road! \n\nI have tried to register a complaint on http://www.kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in/complaint.html, but nothing happens after I press the \"submit\" button. Hence, I\'m writing here.', '2015-11-01T14:34:25+0000', 'negative'),
