('129115403803409_10157092492020626', 'WB02AE7499 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR No Right-Turn, AT SYED AMIR ALI AVENUE/BECK BAGAN ROW, AT 16:35 HRS VIDE CASE NO- ggPC037608/16 DATED 25-JUN-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nI have received this SMS from your Dept regarding a traffic violation, which is grossly wrong because my car didn\'t go out anywhere on that day after morning 10am so how can I be booked for any violation at evening 4.35pm..', '2016-06-27T00:15:26+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10157298955065276', 'This Taxi Driver was too interested to avail the Maa Flyover to go to Salt Lake, as it would give him a hefty sum on the Meter. However, he refused when asked to avail the Park Circus route. Since when are these people deciding which routes to take? Please lodge an immediate complaint (If at all you wish to take any action)\n\nPlace - Exide Crossing, Time - 8.20 PM, Taxi No - WB - 04D 3002', '2016-09-14T14:55:34+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10157370878725461', 'A small self drive of distributing water bottles to all the Kolkata traffic police in James long behala strech. For you and your team the traffic is normal despite of the burning sun you guys stand firm and make the traffic movement normal ..A small gesture to the team Kolkata Traffic Police KUDOS \n\n#Ktp.\n#Kolkata \n#Kolkatatrafficpolice\n#respect', '2016-09-19T09:40:30+0000', 'neutral'),
