('129115403803409_10158003207090228', 'Dear Sir,\n\nI have received below SMS, \n\" WB02AH7736 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Stop Line Violation, AT M G ROAD/KARUNAMOYEE BRIDGE/, AT 14:23 HRS VIDE CASE NO- yyPC030398/16 DATED 24-DEC-16. \"\nAs I recall my car was near Kona express at that time. \nPlease help. \nThank you \nRegards, \nKripa', '2017-01-03T06:22:30+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10158171290780232', 'WB02AC7570 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Stop Line Violation, AT COUNCIL HOUSE STREET/HARE STREET/B B D BAG(S)/N S ROAD/, AT 20:15 HRS VIDE CASE NO- aaPC049401/17 DATED 15-JAN-17. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP (please show us the proof) I am sure there are cctv\'s installed across Calcutta that record the jumping of stop lines and red light violations, please provide the same', '2017-01-16T10:51:31+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10158264085145125', 'Location: Anwar Shah signal crossing, South Kolkat\nTime & Date: 9:30 AM, 26th Feb, 2017\n\nThis car has hit my father\'s car at the signal and en my father asked the on duty traffic policeman to help, he replied \"Ami ki korbo? Agun dhorabo?\" (What can I do? Start a fire?)\n\nKolkata Traffic Police - Is this what you teach your sergeants? To be ignorant and stupid? To be of no help to the local man during a crisis? Shame on such foolish policemen. Everyone could see that the Sumo (picture below) had rammed into our car but the one person who has so called authority to help, had no interest or intention of helping. Madam Chief Minister, what will you do to help? #corrupt #fail #westbengalpolicefail #shame #useless #mamatabanerjee #westbengal #kolkata #traffic #anwarshah', '2017-02-27T04:53:08+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10158378565210177', 'Star\'s Of Bengal Promoting Road Safety Week through a leading newspaper.  Star people times are always right only commoner pays Police harassment.\n\nKP whats your action on this photographic proof please let us know... Waiting for your reply.', '2017-04-04T01:57:42+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10158440517615232', 'Your transaction against Case No - AL17116253, Vehicle No  is processed vide Spot Ref No. AS17031004161 dated 10-03-17 14:47:45, amounting Rs.300. - - - - - -  this you have taken from us for speeding,  you have no clear boards mentioning what is the speed limit one has to follow! If you want people to be more  disciplined first improve the signage of the city!', '2017-03-10T09:22:42+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10158471163700545', 'Hi, My car has been prosecuted vide case no crPC151844/17, date - 24/03/2017 case 09:42 at Esplanade Crossing South. As per image shared on the website, it shows it was for stop line violation. My Car is WB02AJ7311.\nAlso, there seem to be numerous cars together way ahead of the stop line. Some will escape prosecution because they were not the first row cars and so have their number plate hidden behind the first row cars.\nAlso, I take that route everyday to office any time between 9 Am to 10 30 AM. It is a huge crossing and often the signal turns from green to yellow to red in a few seconds after we cross the stop line and we are stuck.\n\nI have more than one car and we often receive cases for the similar incident. I have one for another of my car on another date as well with image.\n\nWe stopped as it turned yellow in the msot recent case but were well ahead fo the stop line and chose not to risk moving ahead when traffic maybe moving in from SN Banerjee Road.\n\nThis is an almost everyday story, and we can not be penalised everyday for a situation where we have no control.\n\nPls guide. \n\nThis is a request as a honest law abiding citizen. We want to follow traffic rules as it is for our own safety,but to be penalised like this on the crossing 10 days a month is very difficult to understand even after being completely careful and following rules.\n\nThanks & Best Regards\n\nPrateek Bihani', '2017-04-17T06:03:16+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10158500241900276', 'Refusal by a White \"No Refusal\" Taxi today... At Shakespeare Sarani Crossing, Destination sought -Salt Lake, Time - 4.25 PM. Please take appropriate steps as per Traffic Law (No - WB 04F 8742)', '2017-05-10T11:07:16+0000', 'positive'),
