('129115403803409_10202168437772719', 'Dear Kolkata Traffic Police,\n\nI have been subjected to pay fines for instances like Playing MP3 player inside my car with windows raised and normal volume, or crossing signal in yellow light.\n\nIf these are offenses, i am happy to pay and abide by. Most of us respect the law and yes, have fear for law. Infact twice i have seen rogues arguing or daring Traffic cops and i have tried to take Cops side. Thats the respect we have. But this picture is a slap on our faces. \n\nA busy Chittaranjan Hospital node, three Policemen in Khaki, one with helmet, rest without them, carrying some wooden pointed sticks, riding on a bike! They crossed Chittaranjan signal when i could try to capture the \'offenders\' but signal went green and i had to start driving. They even went past 4 No. Bridge signal- one of the busiest in Kolkata. None to stop them? Why so?\n\nThe last 4 digits of the Bike were 8100, sorry as i couldnt note rest part.\n\nI as a citizen, dont expect you to anyhow get to them. But just wanted to share, we also are humans but never let go past, even if we have our reasons.\n\nNot to mention the amount of rash bike riders on this CIT road every evening, careless, helmetless...aiming to be themselves or make others lifeless.\n\nYours Sincerely..\nJust another Citizen.', '2014-11-05T13:52:21+0000', 'positive'),
