('129115403803409_10202257701075804', 'I am very much unhappy to say that today an incident happened due to which the faith of the general people from the traffic police will be traumatize. Today I went for my passport collection in The Passport Seva Kendra in ruby more. I parked my bike where around 3 bikes were parked and around 4 to 6 cars were also parked. There were no \" NO PARKING\" sign over there and there were no one also whom I cans ask regarding that whether its a  proper parking place or not. So I parked my bike there and went for my passport collection. But when I came back from my passport work i found that my bike was not there. I asked the local people that who took my bike, they told me that they took my bike in the police station situated beside Science City. When i went there by public transport, i found my bike was hanging like a crap in their towing car. The office in charge was also not present there. I call him thrice and he came back after 1.5 Hrs. He told me that there is a towing charge of 100 Rs which i paid and i have to pay extra 20 rs for his job which he is already getting paid by the government. \n\nWhen i went to my bike i found that there are several scratches made due to the towing process. I am uploading a pic of that. My question is who is responsible for these scratches in my bike ????\n\nThe Sargent should have locked one of my bikes wheels with the lock they were provided. And later on i can pay the spot fine and release my bike from there. But now who will compensate for these damages made by the Police towing car ????\n\nPlease suggest a solution for this problem.', '2014-06-16T11:48:06+0000', 'positive'),
