('129115403803409_10203216261922853', 'Hello KTP\n\nAround 9.30 pm i just crossed 100 mtrs into maa flyover and i was going towards park circus in bike.\nThere was a car at the left side and i was going in around 30-40kms/hr. Suddenly one swift silver colour (wb 06g 4630) came behind me and went thourgh me and the car at very high speed and was signalling something at me in anger  may be because he was disturbed my my slow speed. As you know road works are in progress and it is a bit tough for a bike to go at high speed because of the uneven surface on the flyover and there is speed limit.\n\nNow i crossed the flyover and he was waiting at the 7 point crossing signal. I asked him why he was driving like this which may lead to a big issue. His response was like why i was going slow and if i was goimg slow why i was not going at the most left side. He was very angry and was using abusing languages using the worst words one can say. I stood in front of him for a discussion in presense of the police official there. Police came and asked the issue. I told him then he asked both me and that driver to go to side and discuss. I was going to park my bike at the side. The  signal got green and the car went from there. And i also came towards my home.\n\nNow i have a question. When there is speed limit how can a car drive dangeroualy on a flyover where there has been many accidents in past and also when the road works are in progress. As a biker i feel afraid because of these kind of rude and angry car drivers who dont bother to drive safe.\n\nThank you. Please help me to stay safe amd live longer and please do something so that these people dont drive like this to lead to an accident.', '2017-03-24T16:51:16+0000', 'negative'),
