('129115403803409_10203702730676302', 'Yesterday at 8.30 pm in Mukundapur at the corner of RTIICS we found this only taxi parked at the designated stand without any driver inside. After searching we found a bunch of drivers loitering on the opposite side in dark and many taxis also parked there in complete obscurity bargaining with passengers flouting meter fare. When we asked for a taxi they told us the stand was on the other side and we should look for a taxi there. After sometime a driver surfaced beside the vacant taxi and told us he is not going anywhere. When we asked for a deal, he said he didn\'t need money. Then seeing us taking a picture, he slipped off towards bypass. I am from Patuli and a regular to the area. I wonder what the patients and their visitors to RTIICS must be facing daily. I wish to lodge a complaint against the driver of this errant taxi and request the traffic deptt. of KP to ensure passenger convenience at this important location.', '2014-06-11T06:00:30+0000', 'negative'),
