('129115403803409_10203730281925066', 'At 12.30 today in front of the INTTUC Taxi stand, despite several taxis being present none of them were agreed to go to Garia. I am not aware whether you have taken any action to my last complain a few days back at the same spot, yet another offence at the same spot reflects the pitiable condition on ground. Just think if it had been a patient to RTIICS or their visitors, what agony they would have to face in this terrible heat. Many people from far away states come to this place for treatment, what picture does it portray about the state of affairs of KOLKATA? \nIt is a humble request to your department to instruct the Purba Jadavpur P.S. nearby to keep an watch on this stretch on the nexus of the errant Taxi drivers under patronage of the local political goons.', '2014-06-15T08:37:05+0000', 'neutral'),
