('129115403803409_10204710391426418', 'Sir,\nOn 22nd August 2015 evening, I went to Salt Lake and tried to board one of the two taxis, standing near Dishari, in DD Block, Salt Lake to take me to my residence in Hatibagan. They not only refused to go to Hatibagan, but had highly misbehaved with me. Many of the other passengers also tried to request them to take them to their destination within Kolkata, yet they were not willing to go anywhere. Many female passengers were also present, who were also trying to avail their service, yet they were equally harsh with them.\nWhen I warned them that I will take their photos and will post while complaining on the Kolkata Traffic Police website, they said that such websites do not actually exist because no action has ever been taken against them from there. Many passengers, like me, had earlier warned about complaining in your website, but no action has ever been taken against them.\nThe local Tea stall owners and other residents had also informed us that these taxi drivers are very Rogue and misbehave not only with the passengers but also with all the local residents. They only ferry passengers who are willing to pay them heavy extras, especially while going to the DumDum Airport.\nI have taken the photographs. Please request you to take sternest action against them, with intimation to me, so that they do not repeat their same miscreant in future. And to prove them that your website actually exists and proper justice is always given to any complaints, that are lodged in it.\nRegards', '2015-08-25T11:44:22+0000', 'neutral'),
