('129115403803409_10205170557163844', '3rd oct at minto park @ 0300 a.m. i was riding my motor cycle with my frnd..(to be sure WE WERE NOT DRUNK)..... i was going to BALWANT SINGH EATING HOUSE.... my bike\'s insurance was due for 1 month.... i was stopped my some policeman in white uniform..  1st the police man accused me of drink and driving.. then i told him to take the test... then he was some how convinced that i was not drunk.... then he asked for license and bike\'s paper... i told him that all my papers are ok but my insurance was due for 1 month and i showed him all the papers.... then he charged me fine of Rs.5000.. i told him that fine for driving with out insurance is RS 400.. ( info from http://www.wbtrafficpolice.com/offences-and-penalties.php IF I AM WRONG PLEASE CORRECT ME)... then he and other policeman threatened me that i should not teach them law... i didnt had that much money... so the police man asked my frnd for money and said \" u should help your friend and give the money \".... LASTLY i had to bribe him Rs1000... then he let me go..REALLY..  I COULD NOT BELIEVE THAT HE CHEATED ME LIKE DAT.... if i am wrong charge me with actual fine........ really SHAME ON U KP......', '2015-10-05T11:53:31+0000', 'positive'),
