('129115403803409_10205487804860330', 'I boarded this taxi this afternoon (16th November 2014) from Mukesh Hyundai on VIP Road and asked the driver to take me to the Honda showroom which is a little beyond City Centre, Rajarhat. He initially refused and when I finally sat after a lot of negotiation, he was extremely rude throughout the ride. He then started asking for an extra 50 bucks to drop me to the showroom and when I vehemently denied, he forcibly dropped me off midway. I told him that I would complain and he scoffed at me and said things like \"woh zamana chala gaya\"\nIt is sad that in a city like ours, which otherwise is known for extremely amiable and helpful people, cab drivers have this monopoly and act like total goons. It would be great if the Kolkata traffic police could take strict action against this fellow because he needs to understand that the same people he behaves badly with are the ones who provide him with his daily bread. I am also attaching a picture of his in the comments below.', '2014-11-16T13:55:18+0000', 'negative'),
