('129115403803409_10206066685759081', '#dumdum_station #Kolkata_traffic_police \n#west_Bengal_police\n#WB_Consumer_forum\n#Ola_and_uber_r_better\n#taxi_union_Kolkata\n\nThis is the condition of our West Bengal govt\'s \'no refusal taxi\' - yesterday I was waiting with my family near Dumdum station around 2pm for hiring taxi to go somewhere but I shocked that, a \'no refusal taxi\' - (WB 19G 1862) directly refused me to go to the destination, in fact driver was talking with me very rudely, if its the condition of no refusal taxi, then what you can expect from other taxi or auto in west Bengal.\n\nI expect a quick initiative from concerned departments if you really working for peoples here.', '2015-10-22T11:47:31+0000', 'neutral'),
