('129115403803409_10206169339344813', 'Dear Sir, Today I was shocked to after getting the following message..... as at that time was at Behala and I self drive my car and don\'t understand how my car violates signal at Gariahat. Can you please provide me your CCTV recording of the offence. Rs 100 fine is not a matter as regarding the harrasment we might get into for which many people quitely pay of the fine to our Faster Friendlier KTP. You can also check my mobile no. location at that time. WB02AF5285 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Light Signal Violation, AT GARIAHAT ROAD/HAZRA ROAD/, AT 18:37 HRS VIDE CASE NO- hhPC051424/16 DATED 21-JUL-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\nThanks\n\nDear Sir. I have notified you previously but as this is an error, do I need to pay the fine. Please clarify\nThanks\nDr D Debnath \n9830303450', '2016-08-01T04:49:48+0000', 'positive'),
