('129115403803409_10206517354712897', 'Expect that such violation of the traffic rules ( pillion rider not wearing a helmet, rider\'s helmet not in conformity ) will not be allowed to take place in future. \n\nA movie has the rare access to reach the living rooms and minds of the millions of global citizens across the planet and the size of the most attentive audience manifold when it releases as a Amitabh Bachchan starrer. \n\nKindly be more careful about your worldwide reputation KTP. Regards.', '2016-05-06T10:54:19+0000', 'positive'),
