('129115403803409_10206638545659524', 'Hi team,\nThis is to bring to your notice that this particular car wit da number provided was in a terrible hurry so much so that in heavy traffic near Metro cash n carry around 8pm on 27th May, wher da roads are in a terrible state this particular driver was speeding in and out of traffic n breaking signals.\nMy name is Beverley Jo-Anne Pereira and my 5 year old son and I was coming back home on my scooter when this car came speeding Twice beside me pushing me to da extremely left of da road wher da road is being dug up. Da driver along with two other members actually looked back and laughed at me. Is it so unsafe for a woman and child to travel on the road these days?? I Am very lucky dat me n my son r not hurt due to this drivers rash driving.\nI hope something can be done especially as ther is a kid involved.\nLooking forward to hearing from you.\nThank u.', '2015-05-27T17:03:59+0000', 'negative'),
