('129115403803409_10207009464388882', 'Venue- Laketown crossing\nDate- 1/12/16\nTime-8:00pm Approximately\n\nPeople going towards Airport are stopped by the traffic polices for approximately 10 mins even after the reverse countdown of the Red light became 00\n\nWhy?\n\nBecause someone from the ministry level(probably health ministry) was coming from the other side\n\nEveryday we witness this kind of manual control of the traffic police because of some \"so called VIPs\" of the state\nThey don\'t even care if the bunch of people waiting on the other side have some very important work,or they are very much tired and want to go back to their home as soon as possible\n\nAll they care about is the comfort of the VIPs and all they do is creating that comfort for them by sacrificing the rights of the common people\n\nBut my concern and question is why(most of the time) we cannot see this kind of thing from the traffic police while an ambulance travels on the road??\n\nI have seen many a times the ambulance is stucked on a heavy traffic because that side of the road is on red signal\nWhy the police cannot stop the side of the moving vehicle(by turning the signal to red) and clear that side of the road from where the ambulance is coming?\n\nWhy all the facilities are for the so called elite class of the city?\nDoesn\'t the life of a common man matters to you all??\n\nThe police department has power to do many right thing for the society,so please don\'t waste the power by only looting the common people in the name of fines and acting as servants for the VIPs and doing several other wrong things\n\nTrust us,by doing so, the department will gain love from all\n\nShare this Sudipto Sarkar Akanksha Chhajer Subrata Kumar Lodh and tag others too :/', '2016-12-01T16:18:07+0000', 'positive'),
