('129115403803409_10208191272283129', 'Dear Kolkata Traffic Police , I would request to give strict punishment to taxi driver as he ddidn\'t bother to be patient to drive slow on the lane - R.M. Mitra road. He should drive bit side left of the road but he drove in the middle of the road and about to cross the bumper. I stopped bike as difficult to pass the taxi in opp direction as I requested him to move side bit but he ignore and his taxi hit my bike smoke pipe and it was in a bit damage scratch that bike was very new and he drove off. Then I turned back and raced after him and stopped him but still he abused me and speed off toward to Health Point Hospital. I clicked his face and his taxi plate no. it was on last Monday Date 12 Dec 2016 evening at around 5.30pm  Please see pic attached below', '2016-12-14T03:31:42+0000', 'negative'),
