('129115403803409_10208409337244742', 'Dear Safety Keepers, today recieved the below\n\nWB02AH8228 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR No Parking, AT RAWDON STREET/LA MARTINA SCHOOL, AT 08:55 HRS VIDE CASE NO- ggPC039416/16 DATED 30-JUN-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nWB02AH8228 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR No Parking, AT RAWDON STREET/LA MARTINA SCHOOL, AT 09:00 HRS VIDE CASE NO- ggPC039420/16 DATED 30-JUN-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nAm at a loss, as this is a perinial feature where the vehicle drops children and the cases are lodged. Some serious thinking shoud be done by KTP. In a difference of 5 miniutes, 2 cases lodged at the same location, is it normal ? \n\nI am at a loss to understand anything. Average such cases in front of La Martinere School per year on our vehicle is over 50 Nos, and we know the car never stays there. \n\nSeek your kind judgement and appropriate steps to overcome this menace. More so, this 5 miniute difference 2 cases at the same spot is definitely more astonishing.', '2016-06-30T17:07:06+0000', 'neutral'),
