('129115403803409_10208440931650397', 'respected sir, this is to draw your kind attention that there was a random checking going near the new alipore bridge island on 6th of november , afternoon. \nThe traffic surgeon asked for the vehicle papers where i was found guilty of having an invalid insurance of my vehicle and no air pollution certificate.\ni have lost my bag couple of days back which had my pollution paper and other voter id and few other documents . though it was my fault . \nThe traffic surgeon said that i need to pay 4000 as penalty. As i was not carrying that much of cash with me at that point of time, he told me that he will settle the matter in 2000 rupees..where i didnt entartained him and told him to take necessary legal action against me. in which he seized my DL and gave me this slip instead.\nthere were two traffic surgeons. \njust infront of me , there was an offender whodrove from the no entry side.\nhe was not issued any chalan and instead was let scott free for an exchange of 250 rs.\n\nmy question is, is this how the system works?\nwith bribe and false charges?\n\ntoday i went to the court in order to release my seized documents, when i came to know that i need to pay 1400 for lapsed insurance and 600 for air pollution.\nthe question is how come a PUBLIC SERVANT give us wrong info about the penalty charges? \nthis is absolutely ridiculous. demanding double the actual amount?\nwhat a shame. \nplease teach these dishonest police officers not to misuse their power. And why doesnt police officers wear helmet while driving? Are they above law?', '2015-11-21T17:54:55+0000', 'negative'),
