('129115403803409_10208960990008244', 'WB20AS8424 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Without Helmet, AT T C ROAD/BASANTA LAL SAHA ROAD/CHETLA ROAD, AT 13:05 HRS VIDE CASE NO- nnTW022721/17 DATED 20-FEB-17. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nAt that point time I am there at Apollo Hospital Bransdroni and my bike parked at my home  then how can I be there without halmet? Can you please clarify or give me contact number.', '2017-02-20T11:29:01+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10208990086284479', 'Dear sir,\nI had received the following sms on 05/02/2017 on my mobile.\nWB02AB3356 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Light Signal Violation, AT E M BYPASS/SANTOSHPUR AVENUE (AJOYNAGAR )/SERVICE ROAD, AT 18:07 HRS VIDE CASE NO- wwPC110523/17 DATED 04-FEB-17. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nThis is to inform you that my car no.WB02AB3366 was at my garage only on 04/02/2017. So I  thought it was sent by mistake so I ignored it. But then I am getting sms after sms (from VK-KOLPOL) regarding 2 cases are pending on 23-MAR-2017 and I have to pay.\n Kindly look into this matter as it\'s very frustrating to receive such kind of messages from Kolkata traffic police. How come you give a case to a car which is never goes out on that day. I am requesting you to provide me a vedio footage for the same.\nThanks.', '2017-03-24T13:14:34+0000', 'positive'),
