('129115403803409_10209191528880540', 'Sergeant Name: PR Mahato\nBike number: WB01AJ0732\n\nThis sergeant was issuing a citation to the yellow taxi parked in front of the KP vehicle both of which were illegally parked in front of Ballygunge Science College. The sergeant INTENTIONALLY ignored the KP vehicle. When I tried to take the picture of him (the sergeant), he FORCEFULLY SNATCHED (Isn\'t snatching illegal in Kolkata?) my mobile phone and threatened to \"see\" me. The driver of the police car later threatened me and took my photo in his phone. The numberplates of all the vehicles are clear in the pictures.\n\nRequesting to take steps soon. For more pictures, see the comments part.\n\n(I will upload the photograph of the sergeant if I recover it as he PHYSICALLY PRESSURIZED me to delete the photographs from MY mobile.)', '2017-05-04T11:33:46+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10209261937410293', 'I just checked the Kolkata Traffic Police site for checking pending cases against vehicles and found two cases registered against my vehicle WB-02Y-3950 under 301WBMVR/177MVA. \n\nHowever, you have posted two different cases against the same vehicle at the same spot, within a duration on 3 minutes. I don\'t understand how that can happen. No vehicle can do stop-line violation at the same spot within 3 minutes!!!!\n\nObviously, one of the incident was uploaded by mistake. I will be grateful if you can delete one of the cases from your site so that I can make the payment. I am not paying for both the cases since the mistake is yours.', '2016-04-17T17:16:54+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10209308935347429', 'Dear Sir,  A complete fake case issued. Details found on the website attached here. I never visited through this mentioned road on that day or nearby.', '2017-06-13T09:46:37+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10209309097740754', '30% of the road is blocked by stonechips and sand.... The city and it\'s roads are choked by promoters and \"development\"!!!!\nWith not a single traffic police in sight, a mere 500 meter stretch takes half n hour to commute on Raja Rammohan Roy road between Muchipara and Siriti..\nBeing unruly is the new rule!\n(Picture in front of Pitchkal on RRMR road)', '2017-05-22T04:23:33+0000', 'neutral'),
