('129115403803409_10209498783334157', 'Dear Sir,\nRecently my Vehicle which was driven by my driver was prosecuted for signal violation on 11 August.\nI had received an SMS on my phone on the same day which mentioned to pay a fine online on the following URL https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net. \n\nWhen I had tried to access the website, i could log in to the site , however when I clicked on the same PAY button, I found that the website was not functional anymore.(Please understand that I am myself a software Engineer, hence I know exactly what happened- there might be NO PAYMENT GATEWAY). Also I would like to bring to your knowledge that I have never received any mail soft or hard copy from  the traffic department.\n\nMy question is , if the traffic department imposes fines/penalties to the common man in this way, ((I mean without any formal communication- as I have never received any letter, and the websites says there are couple of cases which were pending without a fine and have been sent to Court)) . \n\nNow , I have no clue where to make payment for the penalty. Could you bring a little transparency to this process?', '2016-08-26T06:00:21+0000', 'positive'),
