('129115403803409_10209596238397167', 'Hi this is in regards to a accident at park circus signal..A man on a red cbz xtreme rammed into my vehicle a karizma at the signal point when the traffic was just about to move.he was speeding up from behind and without any notice or horn rammed into my vehicle,police arrived at the spot and asked me to do a mutual understanding and i agreed to it if the man paid for the expenses of the vehicle he agreed and asked me to come infront and speak as the police walked away he just rode his bike fast and went away without speaking..this is the vehicle number WB 12 A G 7659 red cbz xtreme', '2017-01-09T08:14:07+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10209606492823780', 'A weird incident occured today. I am going with a colleague on my bike from Hazra crossing towards ballygunge. A police personnel stopped me near ballygunge phari crossing. Asked me for papers on telling him that i have got all papers he gave me a case for not having rear view mirror. On asking for receipt he did not issue one. Sharing picture of the challan. Plus in addition to it he himself did not had a number plate on his vehicle.', '2016-05-16T09:17:18+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10209614901826056', 'This is a serious issue... today 19-sep-2016 I have received an SMS from Kolkata traffic police on my mobile stating... \"WB02AB7090 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Light Signal Violation, AT AJC BOSE ROAD/S P SARANI/, AT 10:40 HRS VIDE CASE NO- ggPC055630/16 DATED 19-SEP-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\" \n\nthe surprising part is the vehicle mentioned here WB02AB7090 is here with me in Bangalore, how come the car is sighted at Kolkata violating signal? I have come on a Deputation to bangalore from Jan\'16. Please advice.', '2016-09-19T15:19:42+0000', 'neutral'),
