('129115403803409_10209665031483052', 'Yesterday, 39A/2 bus (WB 04 G8610), diagonally jammed into my tata nano front wheel n stripped off the bonnet from the left side, at 7-point crossing near the island, at around 1:30 pm. The bus driver happily ignored my car horn and grazed past against the same. Thanks to the two traffic policemen who immediately stopped the bus. The driver looked confident knowing fully well that no action will be taken against him except being fined. Only the victim will get harassed in the process n will have to run after the insurance company. The korba police stn guided me to the beniapukur police stn. We ran to the nearby local service centre n got it temporarily fixed so that I could back home with the damaged car. People discouraged me to lodge a complaint at the police stn because no action will be taken against the driver except for paying some fine. Instead I would have to get harassed. I wish that the law had been strict with such people.', '2016-06-05T05:31:47+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10209691578512634', 'Yesterday I went to #Forum Mall for my personal work. In front of The mall when my driver was just entered in No Entry by mistake, 3-4 traffic police came at the spot and #slapped my driver immediately. And he was demanding rs.2000. And finally I had to submit vehicle\'s smart card. \n\nMy question is, Is this mandatory to misuse the #power? This is called corruption. \n\nI\'m forwarding this to the Commissioner & Police  minister and i hope they will look after. \n\nShame on You #kolkatatrafficpolice.', '2017-04-20T03:58:54+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10209704648116224', 'Dear sir\nToday i was spot fined at sovabazar xing for signal violation.  Case No - AD17136528, Vehicle No WB24AH2931 vide Spot Ref No. AS1703221368 dated 22-03-17 19:31:13, amounting Rs.100. Requesting you to verify the cctv footage as i am sure that i have not violated the signal. Signal turned red while i was half way.', '2017-03-22T15:35:27+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10209711811569668', 'To whomsoever it may concern\n---------------------------------------\nI just received a message at my mobile that my vehicle has parked in No Parking area at RAWDON Street near La Martiniere School at 11:45 AM. Case No: ggPC041973/16 Dated: 14-Jul-16. Then it says for online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP.\nWith all due respect to KTP, I would like to take some facts forward here:\n1. Yes my car was at the location as my mother was deboarding the car, who takes my kid from La Martiniere School\n2. Time mentioned here is school ending time for many classes and its a crowded place there. Usually if someone de-boards the car it takes some time and that too if she is an elderly lady.\n3. Is 30 secs to 1 minute time seems enough to give no parking prosecution case if there is no other intention like REVENUE GENERATION. Whereas at Parking area on any road the Collection Agent do not ask for Parking Fee if its less than 5 mins.\n4. Generally after dropping off my family member my car proceeds towards Parkstreet and takes first possible left turn to get into Loudon Street and then to AJC Bose Road and again to Rawdon Street to pick my kid and my family member.\n5. Thank god! I received a SMS this time which is good; but due same registered offence my another car got more than 10 cases and I need to pay off nearly 5K while selling it to Car Dealer. I did not have any clue for them until my Car Dealer mentioned to me the same. And you know its human nature that \'Once bitten twice shy\'\n6. A little more sensitiveness is expected from a responsible body like yours to deal with this\nNow, I deny of the charges placed vide aforesaid case number for the mentioned reasons.\nPlease let me know what is the procedure to void off the charge placed.\nLooking forward to your kind inputs.', '2016-07-14T16:51:31+0000', 'positive'),
