('129115403803409_10209736628230280', 'Complain regarding rash driving against car no. WB 26K 1719. On 15th dec while returning from office at 11:30 pm near taratalla James long sarani, he shifted his car so quickly without indicator my bike could have skid badly but I managed it. It was a private car and driver were so rogue for what ever I am saying. I went to shakherbazar traffic guard but they said it will under taratalla jurisdiction. On 16th Dec I went to taratalla traffic guard they were not sure what to do and asked me to wait till any sergeant comes. As I was getting late for my office, on asking is there any other way like online complaint then they mentioned about below website.\n\nToday  17th dec I registered a complaint on Kolkata traffic police.gov.in.', '2016-12-17T06:38:12+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10209757177022863', 'On the night of 2nd October2016 at around 10:10 pm on the EM By pass stretch from VIP bazar to Ruby I had noticed a public transport bus coming from Dankuni bearing regn no WB11C4026 driving extremely recklessly overtaking other bus perhaps of the same route dangerously and stopping to take passengers right in the middle of the road there by not allowing any other car to pass by. There was a situation when it was about to hit the bonnet of another car while dangerously overtaking. It tried to frighten by repeatedly honking. Can you please confirm and take necessary action\nRegards\nDr. Tanoy Bose\n9830036277', '2016-10-03T02:15:22+0000', 'negative'),
