('129115403803409_10209932222517253', 'Hi ,\n\nToday I receive the following SMS from AM-KOLPOL \n\n\" WB12C8482 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR No U-Turn, AT CHOWRINGHEE ROAD/A T M ROAD/ELGIN ROAD/S N PANDIT STREET/, AT 17:25 HRS VIDE CASE NO- iiPC032650/16 DATED 30-NOV-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP .\"\n\nBut surprisingly on 30-Nov-2016 at 17:25 Hours my car was parked in my office car parking area. My office is in Kolkata Leather complex ,Bantala. If you need any evidence on the same you can come down to my office and verify the same .\n\nMay be there is some mistake happen while noting down the vehicle number .\n\nRegards,\nArijit Seal', '2016-12-01T10:42:14+0000', 'negative'),
