('129115403803409_10210268709371242', 'Dear Kolkata Traffic Police,\n\nI have been staying in Bangalore since last 4 years along with my two wheeler, I got an SMS on 20th Oct 2016 at 00:34 hrs. stating - \n\" WB01AA3916 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR stop line violation, AT E M BYPASS/CANAL SOUTH ROAD/SALTLAKE BYPASS, AT 16:49HRS VIDE CASE NO-mmTW059952/16 DATED 16-OCT-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\"\nWhen I visited your website to my surpise I found there are 7 no of cases against my vehicle. Request you to suspend all the cases\n\nBelow are the summary for your ready reference - \nCase No                   Date              Time\n------------                  --------             -------\nmmTW059952/16 - 16-Oct-2016 - 16:49\nvvTW032913/14 - 10-Jul-2014 - 11:36\nxxTW023337/14 - 17-May-2014 - 17:37\nwwTW024553/14 - 25-Mar-2014 - 15:00\nwwTW002742/14 - 08-Jan-2014 - 72:0\nwwTW111933/13 - 15-Dec-2013 - 11:30\nssTW018739/15 - 11-Apr-2015 - 14:28', '2016-10-20T02:09:06+0000', 'negative'),
