('129115403803409_10210551729724074', 'From southern Avenue my car turned left for sarat Bose Road, the bus of route 221 pushed me right. I had to apply break to save may self. Next crossing Lake rd I waited for signal, with others. the bus came from back in full speed and crossed red signal from left almost crushing two peaple, who  shouted but bus sped away.', '2017-05-23T09:16:23+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10210818872046183', 'These two taxis asked for extra money at Behala Parnasree at 9:30 pm on 23rd April to go to Hazra.  Since ladies and children were there we had no choice but these bandits should be brought under severe punishment', '2017-04-23T16:58:59+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10210928090016175', 'Dear Sir, I am receiving SMS from KTP, stating my vehicle WB02AG2494 has been prosecuted for Stop line violation at JM Avenue/ Shyambazar at 11:42 hrs vide case no-ddPC012831/16 dtd 18-Oct-16. And asking for online payment at https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net. \nHowever, on 18-Oct-16 my vehicle was never moved from my garage. Is it possible to get some evidence? Also, I ask you to verify the authenticity of the SMS as the same is not having the .gov.in domain as in the KTP website.', '2016-10-25T04:30:53+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10210981464867796', 'Traffic chaos outside Brand factory Beliaghata due to both side parking of the no parking lane.', '2016-12-18T06:44:46+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10210998705035427', 'Another case of Traffic police violating traffic rules..  From Science City towards Ruby n then Avisikta at around 7:30-8pm.. U can clearly see he had a spare helmet, still the pillion was riding without one.. Not only that, he was pushing away other bikers quite authoritatively... M sure he had his reasons, everybody does, yet others are prosecuted, why should he be spared?', '2017-03-24T15:06:15+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10211065893541676', 'Please be informed that this taxi driver refused me yesterday. My destination was Ajaynagar from South city  and he bluntly and rudely refused. When I asked him the reason he said \"garage korbo r Ami ulto dekhe  jabo.... Apni ja paren korun....\" And some yellow taxis were also standing there they demanded 150 rs. Whereas by meter it is only rs80 to rs85. Timing was around 5.30pm. \nI request..  please do take some serious action', '2017-05-11T03:59:37+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10211072251074644', 'It was indeed a very good gesture by Mr.amit shaw to have helped this taxi driver to push his vehicle aside when it broke down.....salute to you sir', '2017-04-13T16:53:17+0000', 'positive'),
