('129115403803409_10211172662210497', 'Almost every day, a huge loading & unloading process of Eggs is taking place on main road, at the location- 76/2B, Bidhan Sarani, Kolkata-700006... Please note this is creating a lot of disturbance to the bus stoppage named Rupobani, used by the morning school kids and others in that particular time.', '2017-05-11T02:08:13+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10211279810766257', 'Car entering from sarat bose road next to nepal sweets at 11.28am today, Mullen street remain one way for no entry from sarat bose road till 1pm. Car no. WB 02AG 8902.', '2017-01-18T11:15:39+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10211291450703523', 'Atleast they should remove The No refusal mark om them.\nShame on you Kolkata taxi association.', '2017-01-25T14:04:03+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10211336600073603', 'How police take money with out any case', '2016-11-20T05:29:54+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10211350679503690', 'https://www.facebook.com/safeonroads/photos/a.357343994290647.86797.356585117699868/1144489582242747/?type=3&theater', '2016-12-28T05:46:13+0000', 'NA'),
('129115403803409_10211414060821429', 'Dear Sir, I had been prosecuted for stop line violation in anwar shah rd X raja subodh mullick junction due to unnecessary manual intervention by traffic personnel. The incident happened on 29th Jan and I had since then wrote to you at  dctp.south@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in\ndctp.south@kolkatapolice.gov.in\nwith further multiple follow ups. However, I have now received a traffic signal violation letter. \nAll the details I provide here. May you kindly clarify if imposition of such penalty is justified?', '2017-03-23T12:59:37+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10211433405539916', 'Have received below message\n\nWB01AH5322 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR Stop Line Violation, AT MANICKTALA CROSSING (WEST)P, AT 06:10 HRS VIDE CASE NO- crTW005650/16 DATED 07-DEC-16. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nThe website in the message seems to be hoax\n\nPlz confirm and take appropriate action', '2016-12-07T04:55:19+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_10211522988058289', 'This traffic sergent tired to toe a uber cab with out a reason that to when the driver of the cab is present in the car,  from in front of new alipore ccd where there is no \"No parking board \" and is a parking zone where many other cars were parked  . On asking for id card of the traffic sergent to verify as the person had no name tag on himself , the person directly said he has no identification card . Which directly means tht he might not be traffic police sergent or a bogus police . As a normal public we have right to see proper identification card before producing any kind of legal documents. On asking so the person directly says that we have no rights as recorded on the video . On calling kolkata police helpline (100) he had to let us go as he had no valid reason to fine or toe the cab. Nor had any identification card. In this process 1 hour was wasted and we were harresed.  Who is to be blamed for this ? Being citizen of India residing in Kolkata, is  this the kind of behaviour expected from powerful authorities who are supose to help us at the time of need ?', '2016-10-23T09:30:09+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_10211538216584387', 'The tail lamps doesnt work properly, the car was emitting black smoke along with that a common nature of overspeeding and overtaking. A very common picture for most of the commercial vehicles on Kolkata roads. When will this stop? All around bypass very rarely I see these commercial vehicles driving decently.', '2017-04-13T15:43:35+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_10211559561917482', 'I received 3 letters for \'Stop Line Violation\' within an interval of 1 month.\nAll at the same crossing (James long road, roy bahadur road) and  roughly at the same time between 9-10am on different days.\n\nThis shows that maybe i am repeatedly violating the same law at same place and same time which is not a mere coincidence. I have no other traffic violation charges from any other place till date.\n\nThis suggests that maybe its the same traffic seargent who is targetting me for fulfulling his daily \'targets\'.\n\nI hereby refuse to pay the fine till the evidence of such violations are brought to my notice.\n\nI also hereby request you to look into the matter and take appropriate action against the traffic seargent who is unnecessarily harassing the citizens.\n\nThank you.', '2017-04-07T10:08:01+0000', 'positive');
