('129115403803409_10211568003021957', 'Dear KTP,\nI really don\'t know on what basis you have served this notice. I live at baghajatin and my workplace is towards Science city. As per the case details I jumped the stop signal near highland park service road on 28th October 2016. I sincerely want to know that am I a mad or crazy driver that instead the signal turning green I will take left turn during that peak hours when there was rush of cars from Garia towards Ruby crossing? And more of that all the buses stops just at the below said crossing then how come I will take a left turn? As because we the service people don\'t have time to contest this kind of cases you people just randomly victimize us. If you have guts give cases to the buses which stops wrongly over there instead of designated place. You can\'t do anything as because they have unions which are being controlled by the MLA/MPs. Don\'t worry I\'ll pay what ever the penalty amount. It\'s just to inform you that I had not violated the rules on the said date and time. Thanks.', '2016-11-11T14:42:34+0000', 'positive'),
