('129115403803409_1116223521728774', 'http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/Most-polluted+Kolkata+kills+2.5+times+more+than+Delhi;+Vadodara+safest/1/24641.html\n\nAlso, please check Times of India today stating Kolkata is MORE polluted than Delhi.\n\nRespected personnel, I believe there are few steps we could easily take:\n\n1. It\'s not,  only cars having  >2 Litre Diesel engine that pollutes (decision taken in Delhi). As we observe, the main culprits are OLD Buses (mostly govt buses) and Most Ambassadors, Auto driven by KATA-Tel and TRUCKS. Why the concerned Police dept does not catch them RED-HANDED? As because they are Govt. Property?\n\nIt is more dangerous than shooting a person by GUN. It is affecting all the CITIZENS and killing them silently.  \n\nThey are polluting our city enormously. We hardly doubt any of them has a VALID Pollution control paper which is holding value below tolerance limit.\n\nWe often see that if they are caught, they get released by giving penalty. But the problem does not get resolved. They Keep polluting AIR.\n\nIt is our City and We have the responsibility to keep it clean. \n\nPlease take hard step to compel them checking pollution regularly and generate a correct report (NOT MANIPULATED one).\n\nMost of our children suffer from Breathing problem, Lungs problem. It is thousand times harmful than a Car having >2 litre engine and having a modern pollution control system in it.\n\nWe have enormous FAITH on you Sir. And we believe you will surely take necessary action against this CRIME. \n\nPlease do not allow vehicle to move on road emitting bad AIR.\n\nElse, After some years we would hardly expect someone born in a normal condition. Thanks!', '2015-12-17T06:19:44+0000', 'negative'),
