('129115403803409_1163333423684219', 'WHY THE KOLKATA TAXIS CANNOT BE TRUSTED EASILY: This is to bring to your knowledge that over the past few 3-4 weeks, many taxi drivers of Kolkata are leaving a very bad impression over the passengers. Many of them are found to have tampered with their meters by increasing its kilometre speed by 10 percent. Some of them are even going to the extent by tampering it during the journey. I want to state that as a daily taxi passenger, this is totally unacceptable. I hope you take a look at this matter seriously because every other day, we office goers cannot have a heated debate with the taxi drivers as they tend to become very rude and do not accept their fault kindly..!!', '2015-06-26T03:53:51+0000', 'negative'),
