('129115403803409_1165854316841307', 'Again. Today(17-09-2016) at about 21.30 at Prince Anwar Shah crossing, the KP person keep their DADAGIRI and maintain their tradition. The pillion rider not wearing the helmet. Var me jai CM\'s massage-  Road Safety. \n\nWe are the cop so law an oder in our pocket.\n\nWe take the penalty from the Common People but we don\'t obey the same thing, because we are KP and we create the law as per our comfort.\n\nMy suggestion to the CP- please educate your person first then collect the penalty from the common people. If you unable to handle this thing you have no right to collect penalty from the same reason from the Common People.\n\nI have another question Can you provide me the figure how much penalty you are collected from your people for Without Helmet case?\n\nI am waiting for your reply.', '2016-09-17T17:29:19+0000', 'positive'),
