('129115403803409_1190849874262617', 'Taxi refusal and abusing an old man!\nToday (9th Nov\'15, at 2.33pm, in front of Esplanade Metro station, beside Bata) a taxi (WB04 C8472) was hailed by a very old man (maybe 80 years). The taxi driver had kept on asking where he would go, while keeping the door locked, the old man tried to open it and quite naturally got irritated seeing it closed. The taxi driver not only sped away but abused (unprintable) the old man for no reason - I was standing nearby - it was such rogue behaviour. I intervened and he abused me as well. The old man would be of his father\'s age surely !\nThe old man isn\'t known to me or related to me....maybe I\'ll never ever see him again but is this a behaviour which an old man expects from a taxi driver in Kolkata whom he just asked to drop him home. Request immediate action on him by Kolkata Traffic Police !!!!!!', '2015-11-09T10:34:39+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1192505510801283', '26th May 2016 4 P.M. One kolkata police sergeant Mr Samir Santra. Harass alot... Me n my friend standing near Braboure Road Haldiram with my bike. We stop a bike n put off the helmets after sometime we wear the helmets  and start a bike n going our way... Suddenly Mr Samir Santra came and stop a bike n ask for the paper... we saw all the paper n every paper is ok... but he say he will give the case for not wearing the helmets ... I m shock i ask him we have helmets and we also wear the helmet sir... He say i dont see the helmets when i stop u and ur helmets is in ur hand... After that argument is start.. I told him i complain against u Sir. He say go and Complain anyone or CM. No one can do anything with him... Public also support me but Mr Samir Santra felling shame and his ego hurt... He give the case at last... 100Rs is not a big deal for me even 1000 Rs but This is Wrong they feel they  r Salman Khan of Dabang n Ajay Devgan of Singam but they dont... kolkata citizens feel they r GUNDA.... Please Police Commissioner or CM Mamata Banerjee look this matter seriously before it to late... We r giving u  the vote for Good Bengal not for a Gundaraj Bengal...', '2016-05-27T10:45:32+0000', 'negative'),
