('129115403803409_1195690787185110', '#kolkatapolice on 11/1/17 I am riding my bike with out healmet unfortunately ! So for that reason A Sugent name Subhra Chakrabart (Bansdroni thana) stoped and asked my all documents. But fortunately whatever I have  heard abou Police was Right! The officer gave me a wrong case wich is \"184 MV Act\" . When I asked him why he is giving me false case he threatened me to not to speak other wise he will add some more charges.! A Senior officer was their aswell and thst time he is busy with his wastapp and didn\'t know enything .I told him the The full story and asked why the officer giving me false case he didnt answer my question and told me to go to the court if I have any problem with that ! His name is Biman (so far i have seen) . Refuse to mention his name aswell and ask some other cops stop me asking questions. So is this the way you will treat Normal peoples? By using your power in wrong way? I didn\'t expect any answer now ! Just informing that the faith is no more on Police from now on ! #Kolkatapolice #kolkatatrafficguard', '2017-01-11T18:42:36+0000', 'positive'),
