('129115403803409_1198138480205887', 'Police is known for providing safety to civilians but I ended experiencing a horrible evening coming across this Officer introduced himself as Mr. Dipankar Das.\n\nI was being accompanied by one of my collegue on my two wheeler near Metro Cash n Carry on 20.06.2016 at about 8:30 pm. My colleague was not wearing a helmet which was certainly a violation of Traffic rules at our part.\n\nUsually a penalty @ Rs. 100/- is charged in such scenario whereas the Officer got into unnecessary argument with us and used filthy languages while communicating. He also forced us to pay a penalty of Rs. 400/- for reckless driving which was never a fact.\n\nUpon inquiring about the case details he threatened us for dire consequences even to the extent of putting us behind the bars. This is enough to explain the role of a policeman and their commitment towards general civilian.\n\nGuess no civilian will expect this.', '2016-06-21T13:53:51+0000', 'negative'),
