('129115403803409_1244610455580415', 'Hi.... I am Tapash Sen residing at New Raipur, Kol-84. Today around 7.40 am me & my 6 yrs old daughter going to my daughter\'s school by my Hyundai Xcent car, red colour (WB06K8435) at Carmel school, Deshopriyo park. I drive my car & my daughter sat on back seat. When we crossed Jadavpur University gate no 4, a silver coloured tata sumo car no. WB06K3328 suddenly hit my car very badly on the right back side of the car. My daughter sat on right back side of the car. Thanks to god that my daughter was not injured but she was very scared & cried. I was really very upset & helpless. My car was damaged that side & broke the back light also. I came out from the car & tried to stop the tata sumo. But the driver didn\'t stop the car & escaped from the incident spot very fast. That time I was unable to note the car no but I followed that car & took a chance to note the car no at Jadavpur thana traffic signal. I also taken a photo of that car. After dropped my daughter to her school, I went to Jadavpur Police Station to lodged a written complaint against the tata sumo driver with the car registration number. Request you kindly take strict legal action against the tata sumo driver that next time it will not happen again. Really thanks to god that this time me & my daughter are safe but next time may be the driver run over any people on the road for his rash driving. Thanks...\n\nRegards,\nTapash Sen \nMob- 9836655338', '2016-09-22T08:36:08+0000', 'negative'),
