('129115403803409_1263368833724309', 'On 8th Jan we took a Uber ride and paid the driver in cash Rs 211/-. Today when we booked again from Uber the amount of Rs 211/- was reflecting outstanding from our account. We immediately mailed Uber customer care and we received a mail that it was reflecting wrongly and we do not need to pay the amount again. We took a ride today and the fare was Rs 111/- but the driver forced us to pay 322 /-. When we tried making him understand and showed the mails he threatened to beat my husband up if we do not pay. He abused us with filthy language and insulted us as if we were frauds. We requested him to call Uber Customer care but he refused and was about to beat my husband and take away his phone. We are still in mental trauma. We request you to take necessary actions so that the driver doest not beat up his passengers.', '2017-01-15T02:22:04+0000', 'positive'),
