('129115403803409_1292129684218980', 'Dear Sir/ Madam\n\nThis is to invite your kind attention on below issue.\n \nYesterday I boarded a UBER Pool ride from Baghajatin Lalka Water Tank to Carmel High School Jadavpur. The driver started misbehaving with me and on nearing Jadavpur P.S. crossing ordered me to get down from the cab. I being a lady with a problem in my left knee urged the driver to drop me to the location where the destination is showing as per GPS of the device in the cab. But he ordered me to get down and behaved in rude way. Finally this\nUBER driver threatened me with ACID Attack NEXT TIME I happen to visit his cab and did not drop me to destination even on paying and forced me leave the cab.Driver forced to get down according to his own will even on mentioning the destination on booking.Driver said he doesnot care anyone and complain to UBER authorities or even to Kolkata Police or Lalbazar cannot do anything to him as he is so powerful. He mocked and said he doesnot care anyone including officers in Police department repeatedly even to stating a complain will be lodged against him.Such was the audacity. He boasted and misbehaved to me in the mid of the road and abused me perosnally.I have also informed UBER the incident but till now no action has been taken.\n\nI feel helpless and anxious of my own safety and security and thus solicit your kind intervention in this regard. \n\nDetails in Brief:\nCAB : UBER\nIncident Location : Near Jadavpur P.S. Crossing. \nDate : 6th May 2017. \nTime : 17 : 07 minutes i.e. 05:07 PM\nLocation Near Jadavpur PS\nDriver Name : Debasish. Mobile : 9088233886\nVEHICLE NUMBER : WB19H2642\n\nPassenger Details:\nName : MISHMI ROY BANIK\nAddress: Baghajatin Kolkata 700092', '2017-05-07T05:57:18+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1294796180576295', 'It\'s my humble request to all KTP personnel and  brothers, please please please obey the traffic rules during office time. Because the police car can act as a mentor of all the citizens who drives in kolkata. Because daily I use to see that some of the KTP cars and bikes intentionally violates the traffic rules. And any rules or act have the same meaning for all the cirizen. \n\nToday I have seen a police car violating allmost all the signals from tollygunge to Elgin crossing. Where the PM of India refused to ride a car with red light, then why not we????\n\nThis is not a complaint but a request to all my friends and senior officials try to act as mentor without showing any power which may strengthen the social security in our Society.', '2017-04-21T05:27:05+0000', 'positive'),
