('129115403803409_1358116207614780', 'Dear Sir\nYesterday my father received an SMS saying that we have two traffic violation cases pending in court for our vehicle (WB02AB0623). \nHowever, we did not receive any letter or any form of communication regarding this prior to this SMS.\nAnyway, on checking the website https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net , I found that there are a total of two cases, one in 2014 and one in 2015, pending. Of these, one case (case no. hhPC010543/15) is for signal violation on 22-Jan-2015 at 07:10 AM at the crossing of Sarat Bose Road and Meghnath Saha Sarani. We wake up after 7.30 in the morning, and stay at the opposite end of the city. I can vouch that our car has never been at Sarat Bose Road crossing, especially at 7.10 in the morning. Please can you drop this case so that we can settle for the other case and clean the record for our vehicle.', '2017-03-25T06:41:21+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1358282037517862', 'I have availed a taxi WB 04 E 3242 from Dhamatala bus terminus to Hiland park big bazaar at around 9:30 am on 20th November 2016. But it has charged me Rs. 340/- . This seems to me really high and meter M80222544 which was installed in it needs to verified. The taxi travelled through Parama flyover and the distance according to Google Map is only 16.2 km. But the taxi meter showed me 28.4km. I had complained the same to Hiland Park traffic control immediately but due to non-availability of complaint card I was unable to register the complaint. Please take necessary step and help.\nRegards,\nMasud Ahamed', '2016-11-22T19:07:01+0000', 'negative'),
