('129115403803409_1425443847503885', 'My humble suggestion based on observation outside a school in Kolkata.\nIt is to draw your kind attention to the safety of small children crossing the road to reach their car pool or bus after /before school.\nIn Delhi, the traffic police does a commendable job of pulling baracades to ensure children cross the road safely to reach the other side of the road. \nSmall children may sometimes not cross the road in a line or may fall in a hurry.\nWill it not be a better system for Kolkata traffic police to also stop the traffic and let school children cross from in between the baracades?', '2017-11-11T10:25:06+0000', 'negative'),
