('129115403803409_1426559130725690', 'Sir \nSurprisingly to day I have received a msg informing that my car was parked at no parking on 10th November at 19:00 hrs at crossing of belvidear and backer road \n\nFact is this that I just stoped there to pickup Guest in my car from amarjyoti building and moved from the spot \n\nSir, my sincere request is to please look in to matter and stop such wrong charges please \nRegards. \nC.p.Bagri \nCar no WB06C 8759', '2017-11-12T16:30:20+0000', 'negative'),
