('129115403803409_1426977257350544', 'Sir,\nWB06G2300 has been prosecuted for DRIVING IN EXCESSIVE SPEED (84km/h), At MAA FLYOVER WEST BOUND (MAXIMUM PERMISSIBLE SPEED 60 KM/HR) at 13:49 hrs vide case no. crPC594481/17 dated 5 Nov 2017 . For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nSir , we have sold the car on 22 March 2017 and it was also intimidated to the Traffic Department ,Lalbazar , Kolkata on 27 March 2017 ,  the car was registered in our Company name - Rajesh Trexim (P) Ltd., in which i am the director ( Rishi Chokhany ) and my registered mobile which was there in your system is 9831077149. \n\nSir please look into the matter as may be mobile no. has not been updated.\n\nThank you\n\nRishi Chokhany', '2017-11-13T05:12:00+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1426978074017129', 'Dear Officers,\nToday morning i have got an sms stating \n\n“WB08B1310 has been prosecuted for No Parking, at E M BYPASS/CANAL SOUTH ROAD/SALTLAKE BYPASS, at 10:19 hrs vide case no- mmPC119085/17 dated 07-NOV-17. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP”\n\nBut seeing this sms i was shocked because this car is now in delhi for a good 1 year over and cannot be sighted in kolkata on the mentioned date. Please clarify me the exact number as the registration number matches with the vehicle which is in delhi.\n Regards,\nAyan', '2017-11-13T05:14:07+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1426981207350149', 'Sir,\n\nWB06G2300 has been prosecuted for DRIVING IN EXCESSIVE SPEED (84KM/HR), at MAA FLYOVER WEST BOUND (MAXIMUM PERMISSIBLE SPEED 60 KM/HR) at 13.49 hrs vide case no. – crPC594481/17 dated 5 Nov 2017 . For online payment, please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net – TEAM KTP\n\nSir, we have sold this car on 22 March 2017 and it has been intimidated to Traffic Police, Lalbazar, Kolkata on 27 March 2017. The Car was registered in my company name – RAJESH TREXIM PRIVATE LIMITED , in which I am a Director ( Rishi Chokhany ) and the mobile in which I have received sms is 9831077149 which must have been the registered mobile for our car at that time.\n\nSir, please look into the matter . I think the mobile no. must not have been updated.\n\nThank you Sir,\n\nRishi Chokhany', '2017-11-13T05:20:01+0000', 'neutral'),
