('129115403803409_1427051484009788', 'Need Help!!!! \nFirst of all I am very glad to see the kind of response that we are receiving from Kolkata Traffic Police over this Face Book page. This forum has helped a lot of people and hoping that I will get some help too I am depicting my issue.\n\nOn 18th June 2017 I sold my Tata Nano Car (Reg # WB06G 2014) to Mrs. Surbhi Banthia wife of Mr. Nitin Banthia. The said car was received by her husband Mr. Nitin Banthia. While delivering the car I requested Mr. Nitin to initiate the name transfer process as soon as possible and complete the same within a month\'s time. I waited for a month but they did not initiated the name transfer process. I called them and requested to transfer the name but they kept on lingering. After that whenever I called they did not bothered to receive the phone. \n\nLastly in September 2017 I called Mr. Nitin from my office landline number and he received the phone as he was not aware of that number. I re requested him for name transfer process but he gave me some lame excuse that he is busy with his office work, hence I gave him some time and asked him to kindly initiate the process after Durga Puja is over and he just said \'Ok\' and disconnected the phone. After that the whole of October past away and still no response from their side. \n\nI just want them to transfer the ownership of the car without which I might encounter trouble in future.Hence kindly help me resolve this issue. I am attaching all the related documents and Id proofs submitted by Banthia family.', '2017-11-13T07:41:59+0000', 'positive'),
