('129115403803409_1427298377318432', 'Kolkata traffic police can improve its image by controlling reckless driving by commercial vehicles alone . As most serious accidents occur when mini bus or state bus race to move ahead or a mini truck driving like motorcycle .\nTODAY IN THE AGE OF HI TECHNOLOGY KTP CAN INSTALL CAMERAS ALL OVER AND IF A SPEEDING BUS IS CAUGHT IN RECKLESS OVERTAKING OR RACING THEN A PENALTY OF RUPEE TEN THOUSAND SHOULD BE IMPOSED PLUS THE LICENSE OF THE DRIVER BE SUSPENDED FOR A MONTH .  IT IS GUARANTEED THAT IT WILL SHOW MAGICAL RESULTS .', '2017-11-13T14:22:48+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1427316830649920', 'Case No. crLC382395/17\nDate- 3-11-17, Time- 12:20pm\n\nI show this image..but as much as I remember, after cross the stop line, I saw the signal is now blinking yellow sign, that\'s why I stood up... \n\nSo may I know why you guys charge me for this... If I crossed the road then definitely traffic police gave me case... So karu to karu kya or jau to jau kaha...', '2017-11-13T14:49:44+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1427323520649251', 'I had crossed lee road ajc Bose road crossing taking right from lee road to ajc Bose road . I was stopped by a sergeant of south guard mentioning that I have violated the signal but actually if you go by fact and see just as u cross the signal There is a big pot hole and a car ahead of me slowed down accordingly I slowed down too,the signal turned red by then and  I was In d middle of the road wid no option left other than to move ahead avoiding d traffic disruption to occur for others.hence I tried explaining the officer he didnt listen to anything despite of accepting  the car ahead of me slowed down for the same reason.i have been charged a spot fine of 1000rs and d sergeant rudely reacted didn’t even bother to explain or accept any explanation..below is d attachment for the spot fine and I wish the matter to be investigated..kindly investigate through the camera recording..sergeant behaviour was awful as if I have bumped into somebody else.kindly treat this important . In Kolkata signal if pedestrian comes on way after the signal and we have to slow down  and signal turns red or some car slow down because of pothole and signal turn red what we should do please say so that we don’t become a victim to these illegitimate fines.', '2017-11-13T15:00:39+0000', 'negative'),
