('129115403803409_1427455847302685', 'I wish to bring to your notice this really hard to spot Traffic Signal near Unnamed Road, Raja Bazar, Kolkata, West Bengal 700011\n\nhttps://goo.gl/maps/6JcfqHmNoWT2\n\nDespite my repeated complain to the traffic police stationed at the crossing about the poor visibility of the signal due to the leaves growing in the wire just in front of it, nothing has been done.\n\nI would also like to take this opportunity to request the traffic police to monitor the visibility of the traffic signal around the city at a regular interval, many of which are becoming hard to spot due to the trees growing in front of it. Thanks.', '2017-11-13T18:19:25+0000', 'negative'),
