('129115403803409_1428644923850444', 'I am Tanmoy Ghosh.. I have an #UBER.. \n3 din ager ghotona... I dropped a passenger in MANI SQUARE MALL.. Dropping ta korar por Mani square er samne service road er opor e gari ta side kore 2 mnt er jnno akta important call attend korchilm... Phone call ta neoar porei ami okhan theke move kore jetm... But phone call ta chola kalin 1 jon Sirjent ese amr liscence nie case thay, for the NO PARKING reason... I asked him that \"apni eta spot kore din\".. But he denied.. And gave me a slip of case receipt.. \nCase ti 100 takar hoar katha but he gave me a case of 400..And he had also taken my liscence.. \nMane hochhe ta ki?? Khete poisa kamachhi police ke eirokom bina karone deoar jnno? \n#Chi!! #Chi!! #Chi!! #Kolkata #Traffic #Police... \nManusher sujog neoar akta limit thake.. Case jodi deoar thake to jara offensive case kore tader ke din jara rules mene gari chalay tader nistar din pls... Sradin khete 1000 taka income korte gie 400 taka apnara bina dos e nichhen... Eta bondho korun... 100 takar case ta 100 takar e din... \nNijer <U+09AA><U+09CB><U+09B6><U+09BE><U+0995> er faida lutben na pls...  \nSedin ami onake onek request kore chilm je khub important akta call esechilo tai side kore katha ta bolchilm.. But he didn\'t listned to me... \nPhone e katha bolte bolte gari chalano jabe na, tahole ki gari ta dar korieo phone e katha bola jabe na??? <ed><U+00A0><U+00BD><ed><U+00B8><U+0090>', '2017-11-15T04:57:18+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1428651490516454', 'Minto park is jam packed! AJC bose road is stuck!', '2017-11-15T05:12:12+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1428659650515638', 'Hello, This is regarding the following case registered (ggPC126831/17; 30-Aug-2017; 07:58 AM) against my vehicle. The details are present in the image. The concern is I haven\'t been to the location as mentioned in the case details- \"Rowden street\". On 30th August I attended office at Sector V and I use EM bypass to reach my office from Jadavpur. That day I used the same route to reach office in the same car. Again at that early hour I do not even leave my home for office. And I can assure you, other than myself nobody else drives my car. It seems there have been some mis-understanding. Can you please check and resolve the issue at the earliest?\nI did not even receive a SMS notification for the case. I happened to log in to the page and found it..\nThanks,\nanupam', '2017-11-15T05:31:24+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1428670730514530', 'Dear Sir We are the resident of P24 cit road scheme 55 Kolkata 700014 would like draw your kind attention to problem faced by us from long time and we have tried to draw attention of local police but with no results our resident is located in intersection of Cit road and Philips more crossing and every evening and morning except Thursday and Sunday illegal parking of bike visiting one godman blocks our ingress and exgress of our vehicle generally from 8:30 pm to 11:00 pm in evening and on 8:00 am to 10:00am on Tuesday and Saturday mornings on protesting the parking we become a subject of abusive behaviour and threats from bike owners and their followers even our children\'s and women are subject to taunting and harassments. Would request you take nessecary action and let law prevail and our rights of ingress and exgress protected. Will Look forward for prompt actions our local traffic guard is Sealdah and PS Entally.', '2017-11-15T05:55:48+0000', 'neutral'),
