('129115403803409_1429737960407807', 'Kolkata Traffic police personnel Ghanasyam Maity from Tiljala traffic guard is a shame for the force. Today around 5:30pm I was about to take Right turn from E M Bypass to C.N. Roy road and as per the Signal I took the right turn all of a sudden my daughter told me that the traffic police took my vehicle number. I entered the road and stopped on a side. I got down and went back to Mr. Maity that why he took my Vehicle Number? To my surprise he told me that there is no right Signal there in that Signal when I challenged him he told me that the Signal is wrong. How can the Signal be wrong? while I was talking to him he just let few other vehicle to take right turn. So for me it is completely intentional that he took my car number. When I asked him what will be my case here he told me signal violation. This is the most stupid case I hear that for taking valid right turn you get penalised for signal violation.. can any one plz let me know what I should do now as I know that tomorrow I will get sms of this case.', '2017-11-16T12:32:07+0000', 'negative'),
