('129115403803409_1430434417004828', 'My car got hit by this bus badly from backside at at about 1:05 pm today 17/11/2017 at Highland park crossing towards ruby. My car WB 06N 3341 got badly damaged in the right rear side. I followed the bus and asked for help in the ruby crossing to stop the bus and book it, but the police persons were soo \"friendly\" that they allowed the bus to move and advised me to go and complaint in the police station. I am nla common law abiding citizen who do not want law to be taken in public hand. But such indifferent act by police personnel only prompt people to think that hooliganism by citizens in case of traffic acident is perhaps the way to bring matters to police\'s notice , because police perhaps does not listen to polite complaints from law abiding citizens. Hope that this matter would not be ignored by Kolkata Police. Thanks & Regarda', '2017-11-17T07:58:36+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1430457760335827', 'Dear Kolkata Traffic Police Team,\n\nKudos to your new initiative to send sms on traffic violation and I\'m sure this would not only increase the fine volumes but also make people abide by the rules.\nBut, you made a mistake with my case. The car concerned in the below screenshot has been in Mumbai for more than one and half year and I can definitely vouch that I didn\'t take a cross country road trip with this car ever after. Also, I do possess NOC and other necessary certificates which clearly establish that the car has been out of your jurisdiction for one and half years. It might be an honest mistake or may someone else using a false cwr number. Either way, may I request you to kindly check with your personnel on ground once and rectify this mistake?', '2017-11-17T08:50:03+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1430486456999624', 'This I have posted on Monday and I have got response from department that case have been forwarded to concerned gaurd and will get a call regarding this but no response till date please look into the matter . \n\nI had crossed lee road ajc Bose road crossing taking right from lee road to ajc Bose road . I was stopped by a sergeant of south guard mentioning that I have violated the signal but actually if you go by fact and see just as u cross the signal There is a big pot hole and a car ahead of me slowed down accordingly I slowed down too,the signal turned red by then and  I was In d middle of the road wid no option left other than to move ahead avoiding d traffic disruption to occur for others.hence I tried explaining the officer he didnt listen to anything despite of accepting  the car ahead of me slowed down for the same reason.i have been charged a spot fine of 1000rs and d sergeant rudely reacted didn’t even bother to explain or accept any explanation..below is d attachment for the spot fine and I wish the matter to be investigated..kindly investigate through the camera recording..sergeant behaviour was awful as if I have bumped into somebody else.kindly treat this important . In Kolkata signal if pedestrian comes on way after the signal and we have to slow down  and signal turns red or some car slow down because of pothole and signal turn red what we should do please say so that we don’t become a victim to these illegitimate fines.', '2017-11-17T09:49:33+0000', 'negative'),
