('129115403803409_1430710023643934', 'Dear Sir \nI would like to bring to your kind attention this fine which has been already paid vide spot fine. Yet it is clearly unfair as I will try and explain.\nThe signal turned yellow well after the vehicle passed the Zebra Crossing and the option was to stop in the middle of the road blocking oncoming traffic, in such a situation my friend went ahead and was stopped by the traffic constable and was informed that he had infringed the traffic rule.\nMy friend informed him that he was using his best judgement as the traffic was green when you had crossed yet while he was midway the signal turned yellow.\nIn view of safety and stopping your vehicle suddenly and in the path of other traffic it seems most prudent to carry on and not stop as you are already passed half way.\nWhile the fine is a very minor amount it\'s a greater fact that we are being asked to do something which is not in the best interest of road safety and may not be in line with rules set in place by you. \nIf you require further clarification my friend would be glad to be of your assistance, yet if your investigation reveal that my friend is not liable for this penalty, I humbly request that this fine and infringement be expunged from his record. \n\nYour transaction against Case No - AH17595748, Vehicle No WB01AK4819 is processed vide Spot Ref No. AS1711075462 dated 07-11-17 07:59:33, amounting Rs.100. E-receipt  https://storage.googleapis.com/spotpayment/AH17595748 Your mobile no is your password - Team KTP', '2017-11-17T15:29:04+0000', 'positive'),
