('129115403803409_1433170863397850', 'WB 25G 3456\nTime: 2 :12 pm\nLocation: Before saltlake gate, signal infront of ultadanga flyover. \n\nI was noticing this car for a long time, the driver tried to break all major signals starting from hyatt regency, but couldnt due to traffic, he was pushing other cars off the road, honking, rash driving, THEN WHEN HE GOT A CHANCE, THE DRIVER BROKE THE SIGNAL INFRONT OF ULTADANGA FLYOVER. HE WENT STRAIGHT INTO INCOMING TRAFFIC. \n\nTHERE IS A CAMERA ON THAT SIGNAL PLEASE CHECK THE FOOTAGE AND GET HOLD OF THIS CAR. \n\nBTW, THIS WAS SOME ZILA PARISHAD CAR,', '2017-11-20T10:05:36+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1433177993397137', 'Vehicle No.WB06F3058. Today I have received sms for light signal violation. Case No.xxPC078584/17 dated 17.11.2017 at 09:18 hrs at Parama Island crossing. Kindly note that I was coming from Dhapa side and going towards South. I was halfway through the crossing (near Biswa Bangla Globe) and well after the stop line when the light signal turned yellow and I drove through since it was unsafe to stop midway suddenly. You can verify it through your camera installed there. In a similar case on earlier occasion KTP had advised me on facebook page to drive through under yellow signal. DC (Traffic) has made press statement that one should drive through under yellow signal if the vehicle already crossed the stop line. Therefore, I request that the instant case may be dropped as I have followed the rule and I have been wrongly booked..Sincerely- Sibaprasad Datta.', '2017-11-20T10:19:32+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1433195830062020', 'Traffic police giving fake cases\nSir just now I got this message....\n\nWB08A8994 has been prosecuted for Light Signal Violation, at LENIN SARANI/MOTISIL STREET/, at 17:50 hrs vide case no- ffPC073232/17 dated 15-NOV-17. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nHere time is given evening 5.50 evening and day was 15th November (week day)....\n\nMy car stands in parking at kalikrishna Tagore street from morning 10 to 7 pm and I remain in my office....I have cctv footage to proove this....that day also my car was in parking and I was in office....\n\nWhen my car is in parking in burrabajar area and keys are with me how come my car can violate a traffic signal in Lenin sarani????\n\nI challenge kolkata police to submit the cctv footage and if you can submit I will pay 100 times of penalty amount....', '2017-11-20T10:52:25+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1433269500054653', 'I think Bus RT No. S23A, from Karunamoyee to Dankuni, (WB052226) have just committed an accident with a cycle-rikshaw at the starting of Bally bridge after crossing Dakshineswar bus stop today on 20-Nov-2017 at around 17:50 hrs. After shouting at the driver & conductor to stop the bus to help the victims, the bus just ran away from the spot. Please inform Dakshineswar police about the incident to take the victims to the nearest hospital ASAP. Aslo look for the aforementioned bus driver and conductor and take necessary steps according to the law. As I was in the bus, I couldn\'t do anything for the victims then. That is why I am informing you now over Facebook.', '2017-11-20T12:46:53+0000', 'neutral'),
