('129115403803409_1434151926633077', 'Team KP.\nI happened to receive an sms stating that my car  WB02AG6151 has been prosecuted for Light Signal Violation, at AUCKLAND ROAD/GOVT PLACE(W)/, at 12:50 hrs vide case no- aaPC073769/17 dated 20-NOV-17.  \nTo the above detail, I would request you to\nre check your system as the raised prosecution is not accurate. for the past 1 month and more, the car is not been in operational mode. Hence pls look into the same.\nThanks', '2017-11-21T13:58:35+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1434194099962193', 'This is regarding case no TW112952/17 dated 21st Nov 2017; 17;50 hrs for vehicle no WB20AR8350 (sent thru sms on dated 21.11.2017; 18;12 hrs @9831311267).\nI request you to review the case as I am sure I have not violated the stop line for the mentioned crossing. I found the signal to be open & after crossing the junction I stopped to the two Traffic Police on duty to ask the destination of Woodlands Hospital. If possible I request you to check the CCTV on the said junction to review.', '2017-11-21T14:58:51+0000', 'positive'),
