('129115403803409_1434814636566806', 'Dear Sir,\nToday I received an sms from Kolkata traffic police stating that my vehicle No. WB06F3328 has been prosecuted for No Parking at CIT ROAD / GORACHAND ROAD, at 16:58 hrs vide case no - ooPC039885/17 , dated 20 Nov 2017.\nBut the fact is that I have not taken out my vehicle any where on 20 Nov 2017 and it was parked at my house car parking area.\nI request you to look into the issue and check the case details as the above mentioned vehicle was not taken to that place on that very day.\nKindly revert.', '2017-11-22T09:02:06+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1434871749894428', 'Hello KTP, \n\nI received a message saying my vehicle has been prosecuted for traffic violation on 1st November 2017 vide case no - ddPC048487/17. I had received several cases earlier where I was present at the place and time mentioned but I paid nevertheless due to absence of any proof. This time I paid as well, but then I remembered that I have definite proof about my whereabouts at the said time and date. I, along with all my colleagues, was at JW Mariott the entire day and the car at their parking lot for an official event. Which leaves us with the following possibilities:\n\n1. Someone else is using my number plate\n2. JW Mariott people used my car without my permission\n3. Technical issues with the surveilance system\n\nCan I have any details regarding the surveilance camera images which will help us identify the root cause of the issue?\n\nAlso do let me know how to get the refund, in the event I am deemed to be wrongfully prosecuted.\n\nThanks and regards,\nArindam.', '2017-11-22T10:49:00+0000', 'neutral'),
