('129115403803409_1435516936496576', 'hey just because of one accident. you cant reduce the speed limits to 30-50 on the flyovers ! that is insane! especially at night when there will be more accidents if people are going slow. use some common sense and let people enjoy driving and not get bored to death. im not saying we should drive at 100 but on maa ive seen signs which say 20 and even when exiting ajc bose road flyover it says 20 which is obnoxious to say the least. which ever dumb people are in charge of making these signs are clearly as silly as these limits themselves! \nyou are making these speed limits a joke, really !! im sure every single car breaks at least one stupid speed limit thats recently been put up. \nplease dont have ridiculous speed limits, its 2017 not 1967 when maybe these speeds were just fine with the limited infrastructure we had ! why does everything have to be in extreme??', '2017-11-23T02:50:42+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1435546086493661', 'This is in reference to the case vide no  AU17631787  the vehicle with registration number WB06H2278 booked on 22/11/2017 around 6:30 pm for violating a yellow traffic light near Baghajatin hospital. The signal was green when the vehicle was crossing the stop line. The signal turned yellow just after the car crossed the stop line. The car was already in motion, beyond the stop line and was just in front of a traffic about to move from the road on the left of the crossing. If the driver stopped at that point which was definitely beyond the stop line, the car would have obstructed the path of incoming traffic from the left. Hence the driver kept driving at a slow speed and crossed the signal post. The traffic sergeant on duty have fined the vehicle for violating the yellow light although it was not possible for any driver to abruptly halt the vehicle when the signal turned yellow just after crossing the stop line. Besides the signal does not have a countdown timer so that a driver can never assess properly when the signal is going to change. I feel the fine is unjustified and request your attention to the same.', '2017-11-23T03:43:21+0000', 'neutral'),
