('129115403803409_1437470319634571', 'Hello!\nI received the following text: \n\"WB01AK1336 has been prosecuted for Without Helmet, at IN FRONT OF KMC CENTRAL GARAGE ON AJC BOSE ROAD/INFRONT OF KMC CENTRAL GARAGE/, at 11:43 hrs vide case no- ooTW245861/17 dated 23-NOV-17. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\"\n\nThere are three problems with this text:\n1. The last time I got to ride my motorcycle was last weekend. Since then she is inside my garage which includes the day of 23rd Nov 2017. \n2. I DONT ride without a helmet.\n3. I have no clue about the place of violation. \n\n Since I am the sole rider in my household, I definitely don\'t think my motorbike went all the way by itself in which case the motorcycle would have been spotted without a rider too!', '2017-11-25T09:30:38+0000', 'neutral'),
