('129115403803409_1437579339623669', 'To;Kolkata traffic police. The department has lodged a case no wwTw129032/17 dt 08/11/2017 against my vehicle WB20AD8775. IT WOULD LIKE TO INFORM YOU THAT I\'M A GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEE  IN CHANCHAL ;MALDA. I KEEP MY BIKE WITH ME IN MALDA. I WAS IN CHANCHAL ;MALDA ON THAT DAY. SO IT IS RIDICULOUS TO LODGE CASE AGAINST MY VEHICLE. I HAVE ALREADY MAILED TO KOLKATA TRAFFIC POLICE ABOUT A CASE NO ggTw090267 /17 dt 29/10/17 to clarify but the dept doesn\'t clear all previous cases. So I request to withdraw all cases against the above said vehicle. It is very humble request to you.', '2017-11-25T12:32:02+0000', 'positive'),
