('129115403803409_1437960662918870', 'Want to share something about tonight.\nFrom Esplanade me n my frn took a taxi for saltlake via bhawanipore. driver agreed to go with the meter if we pay him <U+20B9> 50 extra means the meter charge+ 50. There were full of taxis refusing one after another. thats y we have no other option n we decided to pay him <U+20B9> 50 xtra . then when my frn reaches his home the meter bill is 350 so he gave him a <U+20B9>500note. he have to pay 350+50= 400bucks. the driver give him 100back and said that he gave him only 100 n not 500. (i have seen in his wallet that he hv one 500<U+20B9> note n one 100<U+20B9>note )\nthen he said bhaiya i hv gave u a 500note,  not 100. u must be wrong pls chk once agn.    The driver hv listen nothing n demands for money. He said i will search ur car n that tym he saw that he s hiding something. the driver is so clvr. my frn searched but there was nothing. he then give him another 400 n left him. he paid him 800bucks for going saltlake.the driver was also drunk  thats y he said nothing n let him go. wen we take the cab we didnt knew that he was drunk. Guyss today i hv shared this not for my 800bucks but for those publics who shuld aware of these things. \n#KolkataTaxi\n#no_refusal_have_became_just_a_quote_for_them', '2017-11-25T22:04:32+0000', 'negative'),
