('129115403803409_1438058236242446', 'Yesterday, I had to experience the most obnoxious behaviour possible from a lady police duty officer when ,I visited Patuli police station to report a Motor accident involving the car I was travelling in on the EM bypass.\nWhile KP and KTP are trying to reach out to the public, some within the force are trying to treat the common public with disdain and misbehaviour.\nExtremely sorry state of affairs.', '2017-11-26T01:08:54+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1438187579562845', 'I am writing this on behalf of all the sane Two-wheeler riders of Kolkata.\n\nI like to follow rules but it has become almost impossible to follow it in most of the roads of kolkata.\n\nBeing a Two-wheeler rider I face trouble with the different speed limits of car, bikes and buses.\n\nWhere there are dedicated bus lanes in most of the roads but they mostly like to avoid it and rarely maintain speed limits. \n\nNow we people face the biggest challenge in riding our bikes as Cars are supposed to drive faster (don\'t know why they are allowed) and Buses mostly don\'t follow rules (because of their some unknown immunity). The problem is more in the  less congested roads (VIP, EM Bypass) and all the flyovers.\n\nBeing a law abiding citizen, I request Kolkata Police to look into this issue.\n\nI would like to beg to senior official of Kolkata Police to do a survey to find out challanges faced by Two-wheeler riders and decide on scrapping different speed limits for Two-wheeler.\n\nI would also like to request to enforce speed limits more and take stringent action against violators.', '2017-11-26T05:15:51+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1438258026222467', 'My phone has been picked pocket today morning around 10 am from college street market.I have already did GD at Jorasankho police station.Request you please find my phone as soon as possible I have save lots of documents related to office works in my phone.', '2017-11-26T07:45:40+0000', 'positive'),
