('129115403803409_1439234909458112', 'Hi, I am Admin of IccheDana Production (facebook.com/IccheDanaProduction), a very popular facebook page on Bengali Sahitto - Songs, Poems & Stories. I currently have 25000 very active members. As a awareness program I want  to show some Road Safety videos in association with you to my audiences. Please allow me to play some \"Safe Drive, Save Life\" videos on my page. This is purely for awareness only & not for earning any money from it. Please allow. You can call me at 9231041070', '2017-11-27T12:19:19+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1439251489456454', 'Hello! Good evening.\nI live on the EASTERN side of Jatin Bagchi Road. Vivekananda Park is on the western side.\nFor some illogical reason, you allow parking on the eastern side of this road. As a result of this we now have LIGHT COMMERCIAL VEHICLES permanently parked on the road and also other vehicles.\nThis creates a BLIND SPOT for cars coming out of the buildings on the eastern side on to JB Road, which is inconvenient and extremely dangerous, resulting in accidents.\nIs it possible for you to please make an ON SPOT ASSESSMENT of the situation and take corrective action?\nI am available to help, if needed.', '2017-11-27T12:47:03+0000', 'positive'),
