('129115403803409_1439478966100373', 'Today at 5.40pm at Jora Bridge, car no WB 06M 2513, model Hyundai i10 came an rammed into our car in front of the traffic guard present there. On being asked to put the car aside ,the driver aged around 60+ aged with Advocate sign placed as a placard on the dashboard screams saying go ahead and do whatever you want. On attempts to stop, runs the car over the feet of my husband and also brushes past the traffic guard. \nWe on the other hand had moved our car away so as to not block traffic. \nAll that the traffic guard had to say was-MCR kore nin. \n\nMy worry is not financial damage, but what really got me disturbed is that the traffic guard admitted that he could do nothing even if a person bullied his way on the guard and hurt another person. So, what is the difference between us and the traffic guard if both can\'t exercise any authority and not even stop the car. \n\nIs it acceptable to Kolkata Traffic Police that people treat you also like crap and insult u n walk away ??', '2017-11-27T18:09:36+0000', 'negative'),
