('129115403803409_1439968249384778', 'Respected Traffic Wardens,\n\nI have few suggestions which if taken care can ease regular vehicular movement on our Maa and AJC bose flyovers\n\n1: Maa Flyover ( PTS/Victoria Memorial End) : during busy office hours i often have to wait in the jam when approaching the flyover. The reason being daily commuters now stand on the Maa flyover to catch the shuttle and other passing by vehicle. This sort of jam brings down the basic necessities of a flyover which is primarily built to bypass these things. \nSolution : please challan the vehicle who stops there to take passengers and disrupts the traffic movement.\n\n2. Both Maa and AJC Fly overs: please curb the plying of Autos as they fail to match the define speed limit and go too slow thus causing jam and long queue behind them.', '2017-11-27T13:17:46+0000', 'negative'),
