('129115403803409_1440304712684465', 'Many a time I find fictitious traffic violation cases. But this time I think I should protest. Enough is enough. I received a sms today stating my car WB06G9852 has been prosecuted for light signal violation at ALIPORE ROAD/CHETLA CENTRAL ROAD / RAJA SANTOSH ROY ROAD at 9.27 hours. Vide case no-nnPC078485/17 dated 27 Nov 17. That entire day my car was in my garage. How can a car in the garage cause traffic violation.? I would request concerned authorities to look into strongly into the matter and prevent future harassment to law abiding citizens.', '2017-11-28T10:03:47+0000', 'positive');
