('129115403803409_1442526319128971', 'WB02AG1459 has been prosecuted for Pedestrian Line Violation, at SARAT BOSE ROAD/RASHBEHARI AVENUE/, at 17:06 hrs vide case no- hhPC125675/17 dated 29-NOV-17. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nSir,Received this above SMS today .\nBut my car is in my building parking lot since 20.11.17.\nAnd has not been taken out since then ,till today .\nMy CAR is Maruti ERTIGA Brown \n WB 02AG1459.\n\nPlease check at your end ,there is surely some mistake.\nKindly withdraw the  case .\n\nHope you would reply at earliest .', '2017-11-30T17:16:27+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1442596482455288', 'Dear sir, \nYesterday i am driving towards R G KAR Hospital ... while driving i  notice there was no signal..suddenly i crossed the stop line , two of the traffic guards stop me & ask me to talk to head sergeant..when i asked the reason for stopping me they said That i broke the signal which i noticed was blank . The sergant gave me spot fine for breaking the signal. I requested the sergant  to check out the traffic signal, which was not working properly . He very harshly said me to go and inform to the control room about the signal and it\'s not his duty to do so. \nAfter that I have taken the video of signal. This made the sergant annoyed and he came & threatened me saying \" oii  er no. ta note kore rakho pore dekhbo..\" \nI just request you to look into this matter. So that other people don\'t get this type of threatening.\nVehicle no : WB01AK8177\nPlace : R G KAR Crossing (SBTP C11 1073)\nTIME :19:20 PM\nDate :29th Nov 2017', '2017-11-30T19:00:51+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1442923362422600', 'Dear Kolkata Traffic Police team- on 28th Nov my car WB12D5783 has been reported to break traffic rules at Southern Avenue/ SPM road at 19.02 hrs. Related compound number is AN17643296 u/s 184/184MVA, 1988 and fine amount is INR 1000.\nI was not present on the spot, my wife was in the car and our driver was driving that car. His licence has been taken by the Traffic officials and message was sent to his mobile number. Not a single paper of my car was taken. Most surprisingly the document against compound no AN17643296  has been generated against my name and my car - that I was driving dangerously etc. where I was not at all present on the spot.\n\nMy wife was tensed and paid 1000 Rs online and we will be reaching out to collect our driver\'s licence accordingly. My humble request to you are -\n\na. How can I be warned when I was not present on the spot. As per the document - if me/ my car is found breaking the rule once again, fine will be 2000. Can you please investigate it and decide whether my name/ my car should be associated to this incident?\nMy wife paid 1000, I am not requesting for any refund - but want to get cleat sheet against my name/ my car\nb. My wife told me - it was a signal braking case and our driver was not driving dangerously. However, it was her perception. Kindly see if you can investigate and review it. \n\nYours sincerely \nAbhisek Das (Not present on the spot , owner of Car)\n9874439247\n\nTania Sarkar (Spouse - present on the spot)\n9836012827', '2017-12-01T03:59:59+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1442940335754236', 'We are seeing one after another underpass on VIP Road for smooth movement of traffic and pedestrians. Ruby crossing is urgently requiring one which is becoming a nightmare for both the drivers and pedestrians. \'Safe Drive, Save Life\' is impossible unless authority looks at the basic infrastructure.\nWhy we are not seeing to this ??', '2017-12-01T04:26:50+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1442958382419098', 'Case no - ccTW001215/16  vehicle no-WB06K6687(m cyl) I have never received any SMS or any hard copy in my registered address wrt this case.just opened the traffic police site to check the details and I was shocked to see this... Request you to plz check the genuineness of the case from ur end..', '2017-12-01T04:54:44+0000', 'negative'),
