('129115403803409_1443954905652779', 'I would like draw attention towards a serious issue that is being rigorously ignored by Bidhannagar Traffic Police despite witnessing it every morning. The way the autos n the buses create a ramshackle situation that any day any person could come under any of the two. I dont understand why there is such lack of management???? I would like to complaint specifically against auto no. WB 25 B7 187 which did not  bother n despite of seeing me standing by its side ran over my feet. Now this could seem not “grave” but if Kolkata Traffic Police fails to take any action then it might result in some fatal accident someday.....', '2017-12-02T05:00:53+0000', 'negative'),
