('129115403803409_1455448407841403', 'Sir,\n\nThis is to bring to your notice that  a traffic case No. CrPC 105638/17 dated 16/02/17 at 12:17 hrs,  has been imposed on me for violation of stop line at Shayambazar five point crossing. When I checked for the cctv footage on your website I was shocked to see that the car shown was not my car; and actually had the registration number WB24AE2484. Whereas my car\'s registration no. is WB24AE2494.\n\nI have already submitted a letter dated 21/02/17 at Lalbazar regarding the same and have also written three mails to  dctp@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in; addlcp1@kolkatapolice.gov.in; dctp2@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in; dctp3@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in; jtcptp@kolkatapolice.gov.in; sbrtp.guard@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in; but neither I got any response, nor did the dept take any action.\n\nThe most shocking part is that the car which has violated the traffic rule has a number plate which is soiled and everytime it violates traffic rule in future, the cases will be imposed on me.\n\nSurprisingly your department has not checked the car model and respective registration numbers with motor vehicles before imposing the case. I hereby request you to immediately withdraw the said case and do the needful so as to ensure me that I do not face any further harassment for the  car shown in the cctv footage.\n\nYour immediate response is eagerly awaited.\n\nThanking you in anticipation.\n\nSarbajit Mallick\n45/5, Nabin Chandra Das Road,\nKolkata 700 090\nPh: 7044059106 / 9432234732\n\nAttachments:\n1. Picture of my car and the car in cctv footage.', '2017-03-21T05:32:26+0000', 'negative'),
