('129115403803409_1472222959464770', 'WB06J9102 HAS BEEN PROSECUTED FOR No U-Turn, AT MODERN HIGH SCHOOL FOR GIRLS/MAYFAIR ROAD/, AT 17:59 HRS VIDE CASE NO- ggPC095126/17 DATED 11-APR-17. FOR ONLINE PAYMENT PLEASE VISIT https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net - TEAM KTP\n\nThis is to bring into your kind notice that the prosecution of WB06J9102 is incorrect. My car was parked outside my residence at Phoolbagan at the date and time mentioned in the SMS forwarded today i.e on 13th April, 2017 by Kolkata Traffic Police intimating me about the prosecution. I hereby call upon the authorities concerned to provide me with the screenshot of the violation to support the prosecution or withdraw the same in case no supported evidence is there to prove the prosecution. Being a law abiding citizen I undertake to make necessary payments if violation is proved.', '2017-04-14T09:36:51+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1472596099455326', 'Today at 8.58 p.m a white honda activa with number plate WB01AC8486 was crossing from belvedere road railway club towards belvedere road Linc pen factory..In front of SP bungalow the crossing of belvedere road and hastings park road signal was red towards linc pen factory.The scooty violating the signal crossed the road. Not only violating it but drive very dangerously and in speed  crossed the signal.The other side signal was open.The scooty avoiding the signal crossed the road and gone towards penn road. There is no constable in the traffic booth. This signal is very vital signal and the traffic pressure is really high. But in daytime only police constable or home guards are present. After 8 p.m no one is there in the booth and the signal goes automatic and those careless drivers got the chance to disobey the rules. Even when there is a duty constable they are so careless that they even don\'t note down the car number or the bike number. In this signal lots of violation of signal is happend. For gentle driver like me founds difficulty in this type of signaland there are lots of chance of accident which can happen. Please look into this matter. So,I am lodging a complaint against this traffic violation..That time I was driving my bike so was unable to click a picture. You can check the cctv footage to validate my complaint.', '2018-01-04T16:29:05+0000', 'negative'),
