('129115403803409_1477111679003768', 'WB01AG0308 has been prosecuted for LIGHT SIGNAL VIOLATION, at AJC BOSE ROAD/SARAT BOSE ROAD/, at 23:57 hrs vide case no- crTW150781/18 dated 07-JAN-18. - TEAM KTP\n\nSir, I received this message yesterday morning. This is to bring to your kind notice that my two-wheeler (which has been prosecuted above) has not been in a working condition since last 3 weeks. While I understand that you want to show that your cameras/men are working very had to wipe out traffic signal violations in the city, I do not understand how a dead vehicle can violate a traffic signal rule.\n\nSuch false cases are becoming a habit now and I\'m sure that Kolkata Police can resort to ways better than this to fill its pockets.  This is not something that a citizen from Kolkata expects, considering the hard work which your body is putting in to bring out the results. \n\nIt would be wonderful if you could come out with a proof against the above prosecution. With a hope that you don\'t cheat your citizens further,\n\nThank you!', '2018-01-09T07:23:55+0000', 'positive'),
