('129115403803409_1479546018760334', 'Wrong Prosecution of Vehicle No. WB01AE9281 dated 10/01/2018\n\nDear Sir,\n\nI am very much surprised to see the SMS in my mobile no. 9836940001 that my scooter has been prosecuted for traffic rule violation on 10.01.2018 for riding scooter without wearing helmet at R G KAR ROAD/ROY CHARAN SADHUKHAN ROAD, at 16:45 Hrs., vide case no- ccTW057068/18 dated 10/01/2018.\n\nIn this context I would like to bring to your kind notice that on that day at that time I was in train name DHOULI EXPRESS NO.12822 travelling with my family and returning back from PURI TO HOWRAH vide PNR NO.6410073066 DT. 10/01/2018 ( I can provide the original ticket if it is required). Our flat being locked since 06/01/2018 for Puri Trip with family and there is no question about using someone my scooter or being theft becoz i found it as it is.\n\nSo, in this above circumstance, it is clear that the prosecution is purely incorrect. Perhaps the police personnel noted down the number wrongly. I would like to request to see the C C TV footage of that place on that particular date & time minutely. Otherwise I am afraid that someone has using my scooter number illegally.\n\nTherefore, I request your honour to kindly look into the matter and delete the above mentioned case against vehicle No. WB01AE9281 and oblige and abstain me from paying the penalty till I know the decision from your end.\nThanking you, \nRegards, \nJAYANTA SAHA', '2018-01-12T04:13:40+0000', 'neutral'),
