('129115403803409_1490563427658593', 'Dear Sir,\nToday approx 9.30am at near in between Malancha to Tollygunge xng this Sumo driver was driving very rough not only that once the driver intentionally driving carelessly and desperately at any moment of time a severe accident could have been happened. When i caught the driver inside Tollygunje Petrol pump i asked him why he was driving so rough he replied jaa cheyraar chirey nin. Is this Kolkata police ? The department head Honble Sri Rajib Kumar the most powerful and dedicated  IPS officer ive ever seen and i have a high regards to him and his KP team. So i will request you to look into my complaint and take appropriate action from your end.\nRegards\nA.B.Naidu.\n9331863344.', '2018-01-25T04:18:39+0000', 'negative'),
