('129115403803409_1491647450859371', 'Dear Sir\n\nI have received a SMS today at 16:32 hrs that my Vehicle WB02AD7513 has been prosecuted for pedestrian line violation at Sarat Bose Road/Rashbehari Avenue at 09:44Hrs on 20/02/2017 vide case no hhPC081656/17.\nKindly note that,at that time i was at passport office at Aakash Tower,RUBY,Kasba,781 Anandapur.\nCopy of my appointment letter is attached herewith as a proof. You may verify same with passport office.The allegation made is totally false.\nKindly investigate the matter and resolve the issue of wrong prosecution.\n\nBest Regards\n\nTarit Kumar Das\nMo:9432229008', '2017-02-24T16:15:57+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1491688554212747', 'Dear sirs,\n This is with regard to case xxPC084044/18, date 25th January 2018 for Light Signal violation at 8.02 AM at VIP Bazar for my car WB06L5504. Please note on 25th January my car\'s 1st ignition was at around 8.40 AM from Kalikapur and I would have crossed the place not before 9.00 AM where I did not violate the signal violation. Can you provide further details on this please?\nRegards\nSujay Nandi', '2018-01-26T11:02:47+0000', 'positive'),
