('129115403803409_1498597160188553', 'The traffic police of kolkata is only interested in making money for themselves in ways of corruption or for the govt in terms of penalties like stop line , speed limit etc but there is no law and rules for the buses and autos\n\n1.inspite of specified bus lane busses can freely move from everywhere and there is no action on them.\n\n2. Inspite of specifies bus stop busses can stop anywhere blocking the roads and there is no action on them moreover we are said not to honk and wait for them.\n\n3. Busses can race and overtake making the roads dangerous but there is no action on them.\n\n4.autos can turn from anywhere and can move in wrong side without any action.\n\n5.autos can block roads and can damage any car.', '2018-02-03T10:25:15+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1498633233501744', 'Please note this Cab Number. His vehicle was parked at Ruby Taxi Stand. Despite the continuous requests he disagreed to take us to Jadavpur. Even the manager of the stand could not help convince him to go to jadavpur. I would like to understand if we really are at the whims of the taxi drivers. This is not an one off case and refusals and overcharging has been quite a regular issue. Unfortunately the taxi refusal helpline number also provides no help at all. We have reached an audacity where a police complaint also fails to inculcate fear in them. It is not just our failure but your failure too as an organization.  This is just a small example of what we face everyday. I will request you to sort this issue once and for all or make us believe that this is the system and we should be ready for rejections and only travel to places where the can driver intends to go. Awaiting a reply.', '2017-05-09T12:14:46+0000', 'negative'),
