('129115403803409_1510949865619949', 'Dear kolkata traffic police - Just I had to pay a parking fine and the involved police officer said I am not allowed to pay online. So they clamped my car and asked to pay cash of Rs 300. Can you please clarify the process..? Why I am not allowed to pay online here ? How do I know whatever receipt they are giving me on the spot, authentic or not ?', '2018-02-17T08:58:16+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1511199478928321', 'Plz refer to case no.eeTWO61459/18 dt 4.2.18. The prosecution case given to me is entirely false as I was at my Behala residence at the date and time mentioned in the case. I am a State Govt medical officer and it is really distressing to receive such messages. I had written an e mail to dctp on 9.2.18 in this regard but am yet to receive a reply. I request you to look into matter with due consideration. Thanking you in anticipation.', '2018-02-17T15:10:06+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1511869918861277', 'Hi! I would like to request the Senior Officer to install a Traffic Signal System at the intersection of Dixon Lane & AJC Bose Road (Near Prachi Cinema Hall). There is a stiff difficulty faced by Driver\'s in crossing the road & go towards Moulali. Before we see a fatal accident I would like to drag your attention and request you to review my appeal.', '2018-02-18T08:15:46+0000', 'negative'),
