('129115403803409_1513069872074615', 'Dear kolkata police\nThis is to inform you that a group of young boys and girls used to gather just opposite cafe coffe day at james long sarani near chowrasta crossing.they used to smoke drink and other unsocial immoral things in the road and also the lanes nearby.sometimes they used to park their bike nd other vehicles or drive them on the road on such a way that restricts the road and may cause accident at any time. They take the shelter of darkness/low light as there is no street light or its been covered by trees..they dont care about anyone and used to abuse if protested.\nPls take some measures so we the passerby doesnot go through this kind of troubles.\nRegards', '2018-02-19T14:08:55+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1513346165380319', 'Dear sir, my vehicle WB02AG4195 has been prosecuted with the following case details .\nCase ID : crPC710674/17\nDate 28-Dec-2017 \nTime15:12 \nAt location : E M BYPASS/P A SHAH ROAD CONNECTOR ( AVISHIKTA ) (S)/ 301WBMVR/177MVA\n\nThis case is of stop line violation.\n\nHowever I wish to draw your attention to the fact that the crossing in question has TWO Stop lines consecutively placed ( recent photo attached below )  I have no doubt crossed the first one but am well behind the second one . \n\nIn such a case of ambiguity how is it just to prosecute the vehicle ?\n\nThere is no sign on the road that states which is the stop line . \n\nKindly look into the matter.\n\nExpecting a response soon. \n\nThank you .', '2018-02-19T20:31:07+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1513868835328052', 'I have taken this TAXI from New Market stand in front of Grand Hotel way to Chinar Park. Taxi meter amount shown Rs.240/- which is too high. I know because I am regularly going in this way from High Court. I objected to driver \"that meter reading is very much high.\" Within 2 minutes he stopped the car and said \" break is out of order. I can\'t go.\" I got down and paid the amount. I waited for 5 minutes and found the driver went away with TAXI   normally. No problem in brake. I thought I AM ONE PASSENGER ONLY. I CANNOT SAY AGAINST ANY TAXI; AUTO; BUS.....NO ONE WILL HELP ME.\nI ASK YOU ; AM I CORRECT?\nSENDING QUESTIONED TAXI WITH DRIVER \'S PHOTO.', '2018-02-20T11:16:12+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1514071465307789', 'Sir, has online payment for cases been stopped? I could not able to pay the fine online.', '2018-02-20T15:42:04+0000', 'positive'),
