('129115403803409_1514729055242030', 'Sir, yesterday I received a message that my car having regst.no WB-02AG-4795 has been prosecuted for Pedestrian Line Violation u/s 301WBMVR/177MVA vide Case No.aaPC081602/18 on 17.02.2018 @ 15.05 hours. The car was not at the said location at the said point of time. Infact it was near AJC Bose road/Minto Park as we were returning home after attending a family function from Conclave.. It seems either the  noting of the car no.is wrong or the said crossing (Council house street/hare street/BBD bad(s)/n s road) mentioned in the citation case is wrong.you are kindly requested to look into the same and withdraw the citation case,or provide us with cctv/image evidence. Thanks & regards', '2018-02-21T10:35:57+0000', 'negative'),
