('129115403803409_1515944148453854', 'Repeated pointers to double/triple/perpendicular parking in front of Maharani Tea Stall near Desapriiya Park continues every morning in spite of repeated reminders to you. Why can\'t you book offenders who are lazy not to park inside the lanes and walk a few steps? Cut a few challans and help stop this menace for ever. Seems you are not taking it seriously. Not just slowing traffic near vital crossing but ACCIDENTS are waiting to happen and this will not give you any scope of satisfactory reply then, You have been warned repeatedly.', '2018-02-22T15:43:16+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1515976621783940', 'Entire bypass is free \nAnd heavy congestion in Patuli more as zig zag barricades are put up . \nWhat is the reason to put so many barricades leading to such Jam and inconvenience  for the drivers as well as passengers.', '2018-02-22T16:27:49+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1516670795047856', 'Dear DCTP,\nI am a victim of false challan.I was in my vehicle WB02AL6880 at around 3.15 pm at Metro Rail crossing in front of Tollygunge Traffic Guard.However I received message from KTP that my car violated traffic light at crossing of Diamond Harbour Road and JLSarani at 3.08 pm on same day!!!\nI was on my way to 19, Park Street where I reached at 4 pm. Is this the way of filling the coffers of KTP?! This is not an isolated incident.This was reported in the press a few days back.A unique way of extortion!', '2018-02-23T07:21:27+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1517046658343603', 'Hello KP Traffic Dept,\n\nI want to bring your attention to one of the common incident during driving which can cause accident any day. Using high beam headlight while driving at night make the driver blind for a while who are coming from opposite side. Maximum of time even if we will give indicator to them, still they use high beam headlight. In my opinion, this is not because they don’t want to switch that light but for they do not have the knowledge why opposite side driver is giving that signal.\n\nLike all other campaign safe drive save life, usefulness of seat belt etc if you also campaign for this issue, like, “say no to high beam headlight”, something like this. I hope that will help us a lot.\n\nNow a days the average speed for any cab is increasing day by day and in this situation knowledge of using of light indicator in night is very much required.\n\nRgds,\nAD', '2018-02-23T17:11:43+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1517124691669133', 'Sir, with due respect I want to state that I, Prathama Roy owner of car with vehicle number WB02AK8152 received a offence letter under light signal violation with case number eePC042533/17 stating that there was a light signal violation at BB Ganguly street/college street on 30-dec 2017 but as far I can remember my car was at garage on that same day and we have not went anywhere with our car. Could you please provide anykind of cctv footage regarding the same. Thanking you.', '2018-02-23T19:08:41+0000', 'positive'),
