('129115403803409_1517552004959735', 'Thought of sharing a good change I noticed in KTP recently. Around 9.30 pm i was on my way back noticed a gentlemen driving S Cross while speaking on phone from Ruby to Metropolis mall. In the entire stretch despite of vehicles honking him he did not bother to listen to anyone. Tried clicking his pic but could not do as I was on steering. But the moment he took a right turn towards Metropolis mall I saw a KTP came up to him and stopped him. Was very happy to see the culprit getting penalised and the attentiveness of KTP team at late evening.  Very proud of my survey park team. keep up the good work officers. KTP keep rocking always.', '2018-02-24T06:59:55+0000', 'positive'),
