('129115403803409_1519352664779669', 'My car was booked for traffic line violation at exide crossing at 13:38 on 22.02.2018 (case no. crPC838208/18). But the car was  not taken out because of garage door repair since 21.02.2018 till 24.02.2018. Do not know whom to complain.', '2018-02-26T04:08:08+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1519435354771400', 'Why Google map not showing one way routes... ???', '2018-02-26T06:56:12+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1519587534756182', 'Dear Sirs, I first place on record KP\'s drive to bring in or reign in the joy walking crowd on the streets of Kolkata. However, can you Sirs completely stop this traffic menace when pedestrian crossings are blocked like  the one you can see in the attached photo. The spot is intersection of Lenin Sarani and Madan Street. The entire pedestrian crossing is blocked by a shoe shop at the intersection of Lenin Sarani and Madan Street. Similarly the exactly opposite footpath is taken over by a vendor.', '2018-02-26T11:12:46+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1519750618047058', 'Dear Traffic Department,\n\nThis car is out of kolkata for last two and half years now. \nDate mentioned in the letter is 10th Feb 2017.\nThis car has been shifted out of kolkata in January 2015. \n\nHope it is self explanatory.', '2017-06-11T06:47:00+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1519851818063087', 'Dear KTP, James Long Sarani, one of the lifeline connector for people leaving between Taratala to down south is blocked in several places. \nFor south bound... from Taratala crossing till Roy Bahadur road X-ing and again at Matilal Gupta Road X-ing (sakher bazar). \nFor North bound... from Joka to Rabindranath Tagore Road (Pora Aswatthatala). Also, some optical cable laying along the road creating temporary blockage in many places.\nNow for D.H. Road is concern many portions are still partially blocked for Metro construction making the road single lane.\nWhile various work is required to block and bore roads. \n... how multiple agency gets permission to block such important road in various zones same time?\n...can bottlenecked D.H.Road take the load of such huge traffic flowing to and from southmost part of the state to Kolkata.', '2018-02-26T17:21:12+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1520172788030990', 'I have posted many a times in your page expressing concerns, giving suggestions etc etc.\nBut yesterday what happened if I do not mention here would be very unfair of me.\nI was taking my elder son of 6.8 yrs to Belle Vue Hospital. He was having 104.2 F temp (later detected with pneumonitis) and we were stuck on traffic on Sarat Bose Road at around 2:30 p.m.. Meanwhile my son started feeling dizzy due to high fever. \nIt was the next red light towards Minto Park after Bhowanipur Paddapukur signal. Feeling helpless I ran towards signal to speak to traffic police.\nThere I spoke with a sergeant who was just about to leave the place on his bike. When I spoke with him he asked \'where is your car?\'. \nI replied \'much behind in this signal\'. \nHe said \'if you have a red cloth in the car just hold it in your hand, rest trust us\'.\nAnother traffic man said \'it will be okay don\'t worry just get in your car, we will pass you through opposite lane\'.\nAs soon as I rushed to my car and boarded, signal turned green and I was given sort of Green Corridor for one k.m. to reach hospital in 2 mins from where I was stuck. Few traffic men came into other lane to make way for our car also.\nI would take this opportunity to thank you all from core of my heart.\nHats off KTP!!\n\nFrom a father...', '2018-02-27T02:02:08+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1520238904691045', 'You are doing a wonderful job in Jadavpur 8B xing in the evenings while I drive back home. \nWould request you to do similar exercise in the morning - I cross this area around 845/9am and I find jaywalkers and cycle rickshaws making merry - additionally many autos wait in front of Hindustan Sweets for passengers where the road is as such narrow.\nThanks in advance!', '2018-02-27T04:02:04+0000', 'negative'),
