('129115403803409_1521247944590141', 'A very special Thanks to Kolkata  Police, for very prompt and supportive action to find my trolley bag left in state Volvo bus plying between airport and manicktala depot. The moment I realized about about my missing bag I approached the nearest police control booth, the same was informed to all control room, and as such the bus was intercepted at Tiljala traffic guard by Sgt. Saumik Das and Homeguard Subrata Nancy and Bag was found.\nI was informed on the same, bag was found within 30 mins, Thanks to Kolkata Police with a very special efforts by Sgt. Saumik Das and Homeguard Subrata Nandy, this has further reposed and strengthened my faith in Kolkata Police, thanks once again for being very supportive ...Adding photos of Sgt.Saumik and Homeguard Subrata as a way to say special thanks\nOnce Again, Thank You Sirs', '2018-02-28T08:39:25+0000', 'positive'),
