('129115403803409_1523617981012941', 'Dear Kolkata Police,\n\nUnnessessarily harassed by police....  my license being taken away inspite of agreeing to pay spot fine. Police said either i hv to pay online, or else Rs 200 to him, out of which rs 100 will be of no receipt. I wanted to pay right  away , but he said i hv to give paper proof that i paid the fine, he will not take any soft copy. \n\nNow come to the point...\n i took the right turn flank of the road , n realised it was not the right turn i was looking for...  so i obeyd signal & sided my car a bit left to allow other vehicles to take the right turn,  thinking that there could be any emergengy vehicle like ambulance or patients\n   Is it a fault of signal breaking??????\nIf so i would be delighted to know wht u ppl think. Please check the cctv, as my car was the first car in that signal. The constable calld my car to drive front n asked me to pay 200 cash without any receipt......\n\nThank you Kolkata Traffic Police', '2017-05-26T16:46:08+0000', 'negative'),
