('129115403803409_1523867844328151', 'Dear Sir,\n\nThis is to inform you that the following Stop line violation charged against my car \nWB02AK9584 is mistakenly done. Because, my car is parked in my residential garage since Wednesday (28.02.18) night till now. Therefore, I am requesting you to look into this case and take appropriate action so that the charge against my car can be revoked.\n\nThank you very much.\n\nSincerely,\n\nAnirban Siddhanta\n(Owner of the car WB02AK9584)\n\n\"WB02AK9584 has been prosecuted for STOP LINE VIOLATION, at A J C BOSE ROAD (SOUTH)/SHAKESPEARE SARANI/, at 09:23 hrs vide case no- crPC860862/18 dated 03-MAR-18. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net. For any query, contact dctp@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in - TEAM KTP\"', '2018-03-03T05:35:46+0000', 'negative'),
