('129115403803409_1524807137567555', 'I had been trying since a long time to suggest a few steps which can eliminate road accidents to a large extent. But Kolkata Police (Traffic) never bothered to pay some kind of attention nor did DC Traffic thought it necessary to reply at least once to my several emails (I was advised by this message system to send emails to DC Traffic). But I am not weak a person (am 70+, male) that I shall give up so easily.\n\nNow, I am sharing two incredible GREEN timings (the time by whuch a pedestrian HAS to reach opposite side) meant for PEDESTRIANS to cross at two locations: -\n\n1) At Jadavpur PS crossing  between north to south AND the one way (from Lake Gardens to Jadavpur PS way) IS 5 SECONDS. ALL OF YOU HAVE READ IT CORRECTLY; IT INDEED IS FIVE SECONDS.\n2) At Ajaynagar (Santospur-Survey Park) crossing between west to east AND the one way EM Bypass (from north to south way) IS 2 SECONDS. ALL OF YOU HAVE READ IT CORRECTLY; IT INDEED IS TWO SECONDS.', '2018-03-04T06:02:09+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1525848577463411', 'Respected sir, this is Md Azharuddin Sardar.\nI live at 5/2/1A Gora chand lane, kolkata -14 \nI want to draw ur attention towards a regular problem that i face .\nSir I never drive a motorcycle without a headgear,still these sort of messeges is received by me on a regular basis. \nI request u to kindly look into the matter and do what is neccessary so that these cases are written off.\nI shall be highy obliged.\nThank u sir !', '2018-03-05T09:51:45+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1525889230792679', 'Sir I received message that i have been prosecuted for without helmet in 23/02/18 being case no.crTW2172265/18 at Shamshul Huda rd/Quest Mall crossing as well as again same message was received on 02/03/18 being another case no.crTW232203/18 and in both days I was using helmet at that crossing.\nSimilar messages are also received by several other locals and it seems that the traffic volunteer is intentionally booking all vehicle to complete some kind of targets. Request you to kindly look into it and waive the same.', '2018-03-05T10:56:06+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1525900344124901', 'Sir, gotokal amar nijer chokhe dakha akta accident er bapare apnader boli..jaiga ta holo E.M. bypass(Bengal chemical metro station er thik samnei) a rastar opor akta manhole er gorto e akta accident ghote gelo j khane akjon modhyo boyosko mohila bike theke pore giye nijer mathai besh boro chot pelen..janiye rakhi j onader dujoner matha tei helmet pora chilo..o ro onek bar e okhankar accident e onekei injured hoyechen..local P.S. a onek bar jananor poreo kono kaj hoyni..amon ki Ultadanga Traffic gurd er akjon traffic surgent keo janano hoyechilo..but kono kaj hoyni..\nTy sir kindly apnara jodi kono step nen tahole khub badhito thakbo..', '2018-03-05T11:13:37+0000', 'negative'),
