('129115403803409_1526716450673189', 'Near PTS and Turf View crossing , Though there is green signal around 10.40am (25th may ,2017) but bus has encroached left, what the wrong driving concept ,  as a result entire traffic was stuck, at least we should expect  that At least little action to be taken against bus driver', '2017-05-25T05:14:20+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1527211113993824', 'I am a senior citizen of India. Yesterday (06.03.2018) after being informed about death of one of our close relatives, my wife and I rushed to the Hindustan Health Point hospital (situated at 2406, Garia Main Road, Hindusthan More, Kolkata 700084) in the morning through an App Cab. While returning home at 2:30 PM to our residence at Ultadanga/HUDCO more, we approached a yellow Taxi (registration number WB04E 7543), but to our surprise, the driver of the cab, though agreed to go, asked for a flat rate of Rs 400/-. Since it was not in the night, not even in the evening too, we requested him to go by meter which he straightaway refused giving us a cold look. When I was about to take the photograph of the cab, he shouted at me saying that I could go to any level of Police Department but wouldn\'t be able to touch his hair.\n\nSir, this behaviour with the passenger, especially with a senior citizen of India, must be stopped at any cost and the driver must be given a hard lesson so that he doesn\'t dare to behave like this with anyone in future.\n\nThe photograph of the Cab is enclosed herewith for you to take necessary actions.\n\nThanks & regards', '2018-03-06T20:03:20+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1527466090634993', 'A violation was noticed for LIGHT SIGNAL VIOLATION against vehicle no. WB26AL0175 at V I P BAZAR/ on 06-MAR-18 at 16:09 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking  - Team KTP.\nI have received this sms. Prove to my satisfaction that at 16:09hrs I had made a signal violation. As far as I remember I was watching tv at my place when I received the message from your end.', '2018-03-07T03:34:36+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1527580463956889', 'Today I booked a prepaid taxi from howrah station .. the driver kept on forcing me to get down on the gates of Rg Mar mch..I being a medical student kept insisting him to drop me inside the campus due to the inappropriate surrounding .. he instead put allegations on me that I\'m lying and finally he dropped me at the gates saying that he would not listen to me ..I would like you people to please look into the matter.. the taxi number being 6133 \nOther details of the taxi are as below :', '2018-03-07T07:11:13+0000', 'negative'),
