('129115403803409_1530496753665260', 'Dear Sir, \n\nI am the owner of the vehicle No. WB06A6862. Yesterday,  I have received this notice for minor traffic violation stating that on 18Feb18, I was speeding on AJC Bose Road flyover @84 Km/hr while the speed limit is 60Km/hr. I have been asked to pay a fine of Rs 300 within 15 days of receipt of this notice. \nFirstly, I have never seen any speed limit sign on AJC Bose Flyover, unlike Maa Flyover where the speed limit signs are visible. \nSecondly, if there is a speed limit on AJC Bose Road Flyover, run it should be clearly visible to motorists.\nThirdly, I don\'t recollect if I was speeding.\n\nI request you to kindly look into my case and waive the fine since I have never received a speeding ticket in my 13 years of driving. \n\nThanking you for your time.\n\nSincerely\n\nMd Asghar', '2018-03-10T04:50:25+0000', 'negative');
