('129115403803409_1547930525255216', 'Further to my mail dtd 05.03.18 and 17.03.18 addressed to D.C. Traffic as per mail ID provided by you in msg, I have not received any correspondence from your department. Hence I would like to bring to your kind notice again that my vehicle (WB24C5874) has been wrongly prosecuted on  2nd of March, 2018 vide case no. ggPC168436/18 at 13:15 hrs at Syed Amir Ali Avenue/BeckBagan Row for “No Parking” when I am sure this cannot happen as the car was not taken out on that day. Might be there has been a mistake while taking down the number.\n\nIt is not a matter of Rs. 100.00 as fine but a matter of ideology. \n\nPlease let me know your decision on the same ASAP for my necessary action as keeping the case pending for long will land up in court and will not like to get into such hassles.\n\nIf you are unable to resolve it let me know I will pay the desired Rs. 100.00 fine.', '2018-03-28T05:57:12+0000', 'positive'),
