('129115403803409_1548809508500651', '“WB02AXxxxx has been prosecuted for STOP LINE VIOLATION, at DIAMOND HARBOUR ROAD(S-N)/14 NO BUS STAND,BEHALA/, at 09:23 hrs vide case no- crPC915818/18 dated 29-MAR-18.”\n\nI just got this message on my phone about a Stop line violation case. However I am sure that I DID NOT cross the line completely. Only the front wheels crossed it and that too because a bus was about to scratch my car from the back. I moved only after the bus got closer. I tried seeing the image on the payment page of KTP but it wasn’t showing anything. \nKindly have a look at this as I am pretty damn sure I didn’t cross the line completely.\n\nThanks', '2018-03-29T04:22:27+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1548857558495846', 'To\nDC Kolkata Traffic Police\nDear Sir,\nWhere as the compound no AU18819990. I am agreeable to compound the offence and have paid penalty amount Rs. 1000 at Garia Traffic Guard dated 21.03.2018 after unnecessary harassment and long waiting by Garia Traffic Guard. I was informed by Garia Traffic Guard that I have to receive my licence from Regent Park Traffic Guard after showing the money receipt and supportive document which was given by Garia Traffic Guard. On 28. 03.2018, I got a phone call from Garia Traffic Guard and I was informed that I have to go to Regent Park Traffic Guard at 12 o\'clock to get back my driving licence. I was present on the said place at 12 o\'clock as instructed by Garia Traffic Guard but unfortunately after long waiting of 2 hours, Asst. Commi of Traffic Police (VII) told me that my driving licence will be suspended for 90 days without any valuable reason.\nMy complain:\n1. I have paid the penalty amount (Rs. 1000) according to compound no. AU18819990 to get my licence. But the seized licence have not returned to me from Garia Traffic Guard. Why??\n2. I was informed by Garia Traffic Guard to go to Regent Park Traffic Guard to collect my licence. Why? Why?\n3. On 28.03.2018, Regent Park Traffic Guard again harassed me by long waiting, unnecessary questions and finally they suspended my driving licence for 90 days. Why? Why? Why?\n4.Why your department harassing me and killing my valuable time?\nI hope you will take the proper action against these corruption and waiting for your proper explanation. \nCopy enclosed. \nManas Kumar', '2018-03-29T05:55:19+0000', 'positive'),
