('129115403803409_1549477051767230', 'Hello Sirs,\nI need a suggestion. If i am returning from a night party where i am drunk, and so avail a commercial cab service like OLA,does the local police can chase and stop me and threaten me to put in jail??? \n\nThis incident occured to me at aroud 1:30 Am , Jessore road -Dum Dum park more on 30th march, 2018.\n\nI have not here to debate, i just need a guideline, cz till now, i knew i am supposed to hire a Cab and not drive if i have a plan to drink.!\n\nI am 28+ and i see no reason where i can be fined for drinking , in the same way i am responsible too. That is why i booked an OLA cab. But this incident, leaves me clueless as what to do and what not? Can you please suggest, what can i do if this incident happens in the future?', '2018-03-29T21:28:01+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1549758231739112', 'My Dear Kolkata Traffic Department I know you people are very much obedient you are the controller of traffic rules and law but please do not get involved in your job so much that you start dreaming some random vehicle just to meet your targets. I know tomorrow is March Ending you must have to fulfill your targets before year end but for that I cannot volunteerly contribute on your target numbers. My bike is parked at my home and you are siting my bike riding without helmet in Kolkata streets here and there it is like I am watching vikram bhatt movies at home theatre. I need an explanation and prove of this case and if you cannot prove it I want you to reverse this case immidiately.', '2018-03-30T05:47:05+0000', 'positive'),
