('129115403803409_1550836861631249', 'Why we have to pay penalties if the paper of our vehicle has expired just a week before?\nWhy we have to pay penalties if we are roaming in our area without helmet? \nWhy we have to pay penalties if we have had to break the signal for some urgency? \nWhy we have to pay penalties if we accidentally take the wrong route ?? \nWhy we have to pay penalties if the person seating at our back is not wearing helmet??\n\nBring the change in u first then try to change the city #Kolkatapolice . Now who will pay penalties for all these offences that both the on duty police officers have done ?? \n\nI must raise this issue too me n my frnd was standing near maharani (the famous tea shop ) there were two police officers seated inside the car staring at us like a pervert . We both had to make our moves in some other direction! I didn\'t raised this issue ever but today I had to!! \nShame #Kolkatapolice !! \n\nIn the way a on duty police officers are speaking n giving slangs , who are going to take a step against them ? \n\nDon\'t misuse your powers #Kolkatapolice\nN don\'t try to make us get into a rebel \n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/indrajit.dey.547/posts/1681253988625804', '2018-03-31T11:27:38+0000', 'negative'),
