('129115403803409_1551807448200857', 'I was surprised to receive a case of hand signal violation on 30th March 2018 in the morning hours.\n\nI would to inform KP that I was in Bhubaneswar from 29th to 30th March. I returned on 30th night by Ola and reached home at 9 pm. \n\nI would request KP to share with me the CCTV footage of my traffic violation. In case KP is not able to show me the CCTV footage then they shall on their own delete the case of traffic violation from the system. I would also like to know the name of the traffic police or Sargent who had noted my car number. \n\nPlease find below the SMS , my flight ticket and my ola ride details from Airport to Residence. \n\nRegards\n\nSujoy Dutt\n9830269740', '2018-04-01T13:23:24+0000', 'neutral'),
