('129115403803409_1552337661481169', 'Sir,  I received a traffic violation complaint for light signal violation on 31.03.18 at 15.46hrs at SPM Road,  Pratapaditya Road. Case no.  nnPC104304/18. My car no. WB06 F 2220.\nPlease note that my car was parked on the Rashbehari connector at the exact time since I was visiting the Bank of Baroda SSI branch,  Kasba. Request you to please check the video and exempt me of the charges since it is not a correct one. I dispute this traffic violation complaint.', '2018-04-02T02:56:19+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1552384154809853', 'A violation was noticed for NO U-TURN against vehicle no. WB02AF4972 at C G R ROAD/DENT MISSION ROAD on 01-APR-18 at 19:15 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. \n\nSir we recieved this message. \nThis is to inform that our car was in the garage for the whole day at our residence. Request you to please check the CCTV footage for the correct number of the vehicle.\n\nThanks and regards.', '2018-04-02T04:30:52+0000', 'positive'),
