('129115403803409_1553449311370004', 'Hello all, \nI have a small request to you.\nThat I used to travel arround 70 km, 5days a week by bike. On my way I have to avail 2 flyover .\n1. Garden Reach Flyover \n2. AJC BOSE Flyover\n3. Maa Flyover\nThe problem is my shift gets over arround 11 pm. On that time we are not allowed to use those Flyover.\nSo my request to Kolkata Traffic Police please allow us to ride on those flyover s.\nAnd save our valuable time.\nPlease have a look on this .\nAwating for your response.', '2018-04-03T10:07:50+0000', 'positive'),
