('129115403803409_1553509538030648', 'DEAR SIR,\nToday at 5 pm @Theatre Road, I was travelling with my family in my car. When a Black Swift \nWB 12D 2422 came and started overtaking us almost hitting my looking glass. We ignored the car, but a few metres away, at the signal, he stepped out of his car and rushed towards us and opened our gate and was threatening us claiming that we hit his car, asking us to stop the car. We again ignored him as we were with family. The same thing happened twice. He threatened to hit us. This is utter nonsense. Please do something about it. Action needed.The car number is mentioned.  Please feel free to contact me.', '2018-04-03T11:47:42+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1553694664646571', 'To whomever it may concern,\nThe incident is of  just 5 mins back. I was on my bike crossing howrah bridge when this particular Ubercab India driver was driving carelessly skidding right and left like bridge is owned by him. So I overtook him and found him using his cell and earphones on. I horned and shouted but maybe he was listening to music because of which he was not able to hear me. Suddenly he took a sharp turn to left and touched my bike and ran away. I escaped an fatal accident by an inch. I was able to click his pics for proof and car no. (Although not very clear because he started rushing away seeing he is being snapped).\n Please help and take serious action against such driver. There was no passenger in it.\nCar no. Was WB 04 G 8131; as sure as I could see.', '2016-11-07T11:05:46+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1553713248010277', 'KMC had  assigned a gunda as parking personal between 244 Rabindra sarani and Ganesh talkies. I had parked my car in a lane that approaches Rabindra Bharati University from Rabindra sarani at 7:30 pm today. The lane is not fee parking zone. But the gunda in blue shirt came and asked for parking 30/- per hour without receipt nd when confronted he said he will break my car with stone if I don\'t pay. So I had to pay. May I know whom should I complain regarding this? please feel free to contact me for cross verification 9007004907', '2018-04-03T16:14:44+0000', 'negative'),
