('129115403803409_1554432114605057', 'If the Kolkata Traffic Police is very strict with parking cars on CANNING STREET then why not the entire of Canning Street??Why Only 100 Meter stretch. \nIts not only Kolkata Police who wants a free flow of traffic, we too want the same and for that purpose make CANNING STREET free of hawkers and Vendors. We are ready for this. We want that Kolkata Police should not create discrimination. Road is for plying Vehicle and parking of cars are allowed by KMC against Fee.\n\nWe business community hereby request you to kindly make rules for all and please do not discriminate, and intimate us where should we park our cars.\n\nA line of reply and suggested place for car parking is very much appreciated.', '2018-04-04T12:30:32+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1554579481256987', 'This is for your kind  intimation that autos which ply from sobhabazar to ultodanga route charge excessive fare during rush as well as normal hours. They charge 50%-100%over and above the regular fare. Commuters are compelled to pay the excess fare and a protest to this often comes back with a threat. Unfortunately, there is no regulatory body nor any administration to control this menace. I appeal to you to please intervene and restore law and order with proper fare at all times so that we - regular Commuters don\'t suffer unnecessarily. Best Regards. Thank you.', '2018-04-04T15:27:36+0000', 'neutral'),
