('129115403803409_1559283094119959', 'Dear Sir,\n\nJust now I have got a message from Kolkata police about signal violation notice of my car WB06K4100 at 7 point park circus. \n\nBut the the fact is I am now in Medinipur with my car. Unfortunately I got the bellow Sms. I am requesting you please consider the fact and kindly dismis the case as soon as possible.\n\nA violation was noticed for LIGHT SIGNAL VIOLATION against vehicle no. WB06K4100 at 7 POINT CROSSING/ on 09-APR-18 at 17:33 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking  - Team KTP\n\nKindly do the needful.\n\nRegards\nRaushan Alam\n09735507957', '2018-04-09T13:02:32+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1559503907431211', 'This video is not very rare in our city.', '2018-04-09T17:59:09+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1559971627384439', 'Request attention of the higher authority of KTP.\n\nBeing a son of a retired police officer (departed), I have highest regard for any Police department. Also, I used to take pride of Kolkata Traffic Police (specially Sergeants) while I was working in other cities of India. \n\nLot have been changed recently as per my observation. Many Sergeants (with bunch of civic volunteers/constables) are targeting commercial vehicles to make money in a illegal way (read \"Bribe\"). Sergeants are randomly stopping commercial vehicles and finding ways to threat the driver for a high amount of traffic case. Since most of the commercial drivers are worried about their livelihood, they get scared and mostly never challenge  even they are at no fault. Then the bribe part starts. The assistants around the sergeant start making the deal. They often say in a way like - \"If authenticate case is given, you have to pay fine of 1200 rs. How about you pay 400/500/800 etc and get lost without any receipt\". EIntire amount goes to their pocket. \n\nIs doing legit business (through commercial vehicles) a offence ? \n\nPlease STOP \"Bribe\" practice and do not let down the prestige of Police department. It hurts me at a personal level since my father was my hero as a Police officer.', '2018-04-10T06:33:05+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1559983537383248', 'I got an SMS in my mobile that my car violated stop line near Aurobindo Sarani and APC road junction. The case no : crPC936138/18. I just wanted to bring in notice that it was my car and I was driving to office that time. However I crossed the stop line (Though its not well designated) while the signal was green and there is an auto rickshaw in front of my car. Immediately I reached to the junction (I passed the junction by 2/3 ft in green light) the traffic light turned Amber and immediately to Red. What I learnt from traffic rule that if I have crossed stop line in green and traffic light goes to Amber I should not stop. Though I stopped as the oncoming traffic in APC road started moving and it was not safe to cross. It was not possible for me to move back as there was already traffic behind my vehicle. As I told earlier there was an auto in front of me, it took an U turn and went to hatibagan side which i think illegal. Being said all these I request the authority to validate my complain wrt the traffic police or CCTV footage whatever available and take necessary action.', '2018-04-10T06:54:40+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1560084207373181', 'Communist party cadres stranded the Kalamandir road towards park street. Stranded commuters and general public started getting agitated. Exceptional patience and tactics shown by Kolkata Traffic Police in clearing the road within 15 mins. Two Vans of Cadres arrested for illegal rallying and road blocking.\n\nSaw some office goers shaking hands with cops and thanking them for the relief.\n\nGreat job KTP. \n\n#ChangingTimes\n#NoProcessionOnPublicRoads\n#ThanksKolkataPolice', '2018-04-10T09:49:03+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1560140694034199', 'Dear Sir,\n\nCan you please check the case no. crTW259791/18 dtd 17.03.2018, I have stop my motorcycle due to sudden Red light appeared on the crossing, so I was unable to stop my moving two wheeler immediately and cross the stop line little bit.  But, not violated the signal.', '2018-04-10T11:16:50+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1560142534034015', 'Respected Sir\nI received this traffic violation case in spite of the fact that I am in my office and my scooter is parked at my place. I tried to pay but the site shows no pending cases. \nThis is to bring to your notice that, this case has been wrongly registered against me yet I shall comply and pay for the same.', '2018-04-10T11:20:11+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1560171837372426', 'https://www.facebook.com/1368491616540450/photos/a.1371351029587842.1073741828.1368491616540450/1560169840705959/?type=3&theater', '2017-03-10T02:59:14+0000', 'NA'),
('129115403803409_1560845347297067', 'I got a no parking fine stuck on my windshield for parking in a location where there was no \"No Parking\" sign. That\'s fine  - will pay fine, used to it now. But at the same location this car has been parked for last so many hours but no sticker. Why - because it has a POLICE plackard strategically placed on the dash, of course. Everyday i see vehicles with police insignia violating traffic rules- no helmet, wrong side driving, signal jumping, stop line crossing and overall rash driving - so much for #safedrivesavelife. Is anyone watching?', '2018-04-11T04:39:52+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1560890267292575', 'Dear sir / madam,\nI want to know that if somebody feels that he has been wrongly penalized on the road or the compounding officer is asking for bribery, then what is the process and what steps can he taken further to assure the correct justice?  Can he ask for the CCTV footage if the incident happens at and traffic signal and CCTV cameras are available at the point? If yes then from where and how can he ask for the footage?', '2018-04-11T05:57:58+0000', 'positive'),
