('129115403803409_1561906983857570', 'A violation was noticed for NO PARKING against vehicle no. WB02AH9092 at MODERN HIGH SCHOOL FOR GIRLS/MAYFAIR ROAD on 12-APR-18 at 11:46 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Team KTP\n\nJUST TIME TAKEN TO GET DOWN FROM A CAR BECOMES A VIOLATION? IS A PERSON SUPPOSED TO JUMP OUT OF A MOVING CAR?', '2018-04-12T06:24:50+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1561932723854996', 'Today morning i stopped a no refusal taxi for RG KAR MEDICAL EMERGENCY BUILDING as my mother fell and had a fracture on her shoulder but the driver refused to go there. When i asked him for a reason he just ran away. I hope KP will take necessary action against the driver.', '2018-04-12T07:16:11+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1561940497187552', 'Sir \nKindly look upon the matter. \nI was in dr  S S chaterjee heart unit centre  at the given time and my bike was parked outside the main gate of the hospital. \nI can prove my attendence there. \n\nThis violation is totally unacceptable. \n\nA violation was noticed for WITHOUT HELMET against vehicle no. WB01AK9956 at TOP OF NO 4 BRIDGE/ on 12-APR-18 at 11:39 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking  - Team KTP', '2018-04-12T07:32:28+0000', 'positive'),
