('129115403803409_1562068307174771', 'Just got the sms alert as given below.\nWhen I was crossing the vehicles before me was in a very slow pace and in the middle the light turned Yellow.\nI had no options to stop at the middle. I am sure the CCTV footage will justify my version. Hoping to get a prompt reply from your team.\nMy vehicle number is WB06 H0627.\nRegards \nKunal Basu\n9433240965\n\nA violation was noticed for LIGHT SIGNAL VIOLATION against vehicle no. WB06H0627 at RASHBEHARI AVENUE/JATIN BAGCHI ROAD on 12-APR-18 at 16:40 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking  - Team KTP', '2018-04-12T11:19:04+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1562100053838263', 'Respected Kolkata Traffic Team,\n\nFirst of all thank you for all the hard work you do keep our City of Joy moving 365 days in a year.\n\nThis is to bring your notice that the Traffic signal of Raja Dinendra Street and Aurobinda Sarani Near khanna has some synchronization problem which I have noticed. When the RIGHT TURN signal is green for the vehicles from gouribari/ultadanga to khanna ideally the signal should be RED for the vehicles from khanna to Ultadanga at Aurobinda Sarani . But everyday when I commute to home I can see that both the signal have been simultaneously becoming green and thus it is causing not so safe situation for the vehicles turning right from Aurobinda Sarani to Raja Dinendra Street. I have already faced this two times when onboard a CAB where driver has to break very quickly and firmly to avoid any collision.\n\nPlease review this situation and I hope if signal sequence have been corrected we can ensure proper safety in this location.\n\nThanks,\n\nYours Faithfully,\nSabarna Mazumder', '2018-04-12T12:07:04+0000', 'negative'),
('129115403803409_1562105737171028', 'I don\'t know how much attention it will bring, cause for the first time I faced this kind of problem and complaining here. From Tollygunge to airport I booked a yellow taxi and the route was via Ruby to baguiati and then airrporr. But the meter amount came it blew my mind. Just was running out of time I said the taxi driver that something is wrong with his meter and  he started southing, and I was running of time. So clicked the meter after dropping me to my destination (Kolkata airport). And clicked the taxi number to and he admitted this taxi is from Tollygunge stand. Sharing those pictures and hoping for some action and initiative from our respective Kolkata traffic police department. Thank you. And unfortunately I found that the click of that meter is not in my gallery . Some how it didn\'t save in my phone. The fare was 624', '2018-04-12T12:15:58+0000', 'positive'),
