('129115403803409_1562547120460223', 'Hi, I think the new screens installed at some places , like the one near quest mall and especially the one at golpark crossing, are too bright and they actually cause drivers and pedestrians problems rather than help with the messages they broadcast. It literally blinds people who look at them. I am talking about the new monitors that display videos. I hope you guys please look into this and reduce the brightness of these screens or they might actually cause more accidents rather than prevent them. Thank you.', '2018-04-12T22:31:09+0000', 'positive'),
