('129115403803409_1563354597046142', 'Dear Sir,\n\nAs told in yesterday\'s news by Taxi Unions secretary and other\'s that passengers will not face any problem to go to their office due to Bandh - All citizens of our state were promised that they will many taxis in the road, today morning I and wife were going to office as per normal day, we called this taxi from Sambhunath Pandit Road gol mandir to go towards rashbehari but the taxi refused to go when asked several times demanded for Rs250/- fare for Elgin to Rashbehari..Same incident happened with another taxi the pic for which I am sharing in other post-i would like to request you all and government that please try to keep promises given to us since we went for the office today thinking that our governments police will take care of us but no one was there to help..Please give some good lessons to thus taxi drivers.', '2018-04-13T14:50:58+0000', 'positive'),
