('129115403803409_1567020176679584', 'Dear KTP\n\nI received the following messege this morning.\n\n\"A violation was noticed for WITHOUT HELMET against vehicle no. WB20AV2449 at UPENDRA BANERJEE ROAD/PARNASHREE on 17-APR-18 at 09:20 hrs. Please be cautious while driving. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking  - Team KTP\"\n\nI had just started my daily Ola corporate ride at 8:50 am today from my home at Garia to my office at Sector V alongwith 3 of my colleagues when I received the above message and I was very surprised. \n\nMy ola ride receipt is attached herewith which clearly proves that I was on ride from 8:50 am to 10:07 am and my colleagues are the witnesses. The only other person at my home today is my wife who does not even have a learner license. My bike has moved nowhere today from the parking lot at our housing complex at Model town, Balia and the security guards are the witnesses.\n\nSo, neither me nor my bike was anywhere near Parnashree at the time mentioned at your message. If a case has been registered against my bike, I request to withdraw the same. \n\nRegards', '2018-04-17T11:36:26+0000', 'positive'),
