('129115403803409_1567607136620888', 'Used extreme slang language when I asked the auto driver to start the auto as he kept me awaited for 10 minutes in his auto. I had boarded the auto from South city mall at around 7.10am and after reaching at Lake gardens he kept me awaited for 10mins appx. And when I got down from his auto he demanded the fare. And I told him I will not pay you since you kept me awaited. Seeing to that he started using abusive languages. I found it very unsafe to answer him back and also to note down his auto number. And wisely chose to board the bus for metro from Lake gardens around 7.22am. I couldn\'t note down the auto number. The auto is of the route of jadavpur to rabindra sarowar metro. Please see to the matter at earliest as these incidents are happening at maxim in this route. The auto driver is thin,middle aged, chews tobacco, average height, gloomy eyes and looks approximately like a criminal. \nI couldn\'t Lodge the complaint on the traffic guard website as I did not have the auto number. Please see to the matter as the hooliganism of these auto goons are proliferating day by day.. \nHope to see a quick action taken by the kolkata police. Also please make sure there is enough police available in the morning time so that we could seek their help if necessary.. \nThank you \nRegards\nSulagna Biswas', '2018-04-18T02:23:01+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1567641326617469', 'Hi...\nI have to cross Central avenue everyday to my office at SSKM hosp from north kolkata. Recently police has created a separate bus-way by putting barriers along the sides of the road. Thats fine. But ultimately very few buses use that stretch unless some traffic police petrol the area. Consequently all those bus lanes becoming free zones for parking and pedestrians walking, and ultimately the available road space is reduced. \nPls be strict so that buses use that lane always, or else those barriers can be uprooted and put some yellow line so that ultimate road space doesn\'t get wasted. \nJust giving my thought, do consider if possible.\nThanks......', '2018-04-18T03:26:45+0000', 'neutral'),
