('129115403803409_1568889763159292', 'Today around 15 to 6 in the evening I was coming home from rajarhat by Maa setu. While in the midway a kite flying thread rubbed on my face. On the sudden event I almost lost control while trying to get rid of it. As I was riding slow and was going by the left side, I somehow managed to stop the bike and avoided fatal consequences. I am fortunate to survive but for some minor cut marks on my nose and below the right eye. I was following news on similar incidents for last few months and tiday I am myself the victim. Apparently though it looks to be an inadvertent event, but the frequency of this event instigating a thought that it may be a deliberate action by few anti social localites. They nay be doing this just for sheer fun. As far as I know already two lives are lost in a similar event. And today it might be me. By the grace of Maa Durga and Baba Loknath I survived. I request you to keep a vigil on this and punish the culprits immediately to stop this nonsense. I have never even thought of any such ebmvent in no flyover or road in Kolkata. Hope to see an immediate action and update on this.', '2018-04-19T14:10:26+0000', 'neutral'),
('129115403803409_1568901343158134', 'I have received  a stop line violation I\nCase in my mobile which I was clearly standing behind the stop line ,I have seen the image downloaded from the website ,clearly seen I have not violated the cross line  .I request Kolkata traffic police to rectify the system error as soon as possible.\nCase details as follows:-\nWB20AH5293 has been prosecuted for STOP LINE VIOLATION, at C R AVENUE/G C AVENUE/, at 19:17 hrs vide case no- crTW330339/18 dated 19-APR-18. For online payment please visit https://kolkatatrafficpolice.net. For any query, contact dctp@kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in. Download Kolkata Police Bondhu App (https://goo.gl/Mz9zZb) and Smart Parking App (https://goo.gl/aB2DJb) from Play store for hassle free parking - TEAM KTP', '2018-04-19T14:27:01+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1568927496488852', 'Case no. wwPC218972/18\nVehicle Regn. WB02AJ7499\nCase date: 6th April 2018\nSMS received: 12th April 2018\n\n1. Already emailed this complaint few days back (according to your most lovable post mentioned here) with no response from your end : If any particular case seems unjustified, you may report the matter within 15 days of receiving the SMS/NOTICE in a specified format. Details given in the link: http://kolkatatrafficpolice.gov.in/Traffic%20Enforcement%20Policy.pdf. Regards.\n2. My vehicle was not present at the spot during the time of the claimed penalty. I have a video evidence of its presence in my house parking lot at that time.\n3. The light signal viotation has been logged on a free left turn. What a joke!\n\nAwaiting your response to withdraw the case either due to the email I have sent earlier or by virtue of this post. Tomorrow please don\'t tell me it have been beyond 15 days and your evidences are wiped off and thus cannot do anything about it.', '2018-04-19T15:02:17+0000', 'positive'),
('129115403803409_1568941506487451', 'Sir/Ma’am,\nI was travelling back from my office today evening at around 8PM. While coming towards City centre 2 from technopolis, on the way near to Pride hotel crossing, Rajarhat a biker JH05AJ7791 was continually driving in an unruly way. In return I told him to drive properly. On the contrary, he followed me till near CC2, and also banged my Car window several times in the crossing. For my security, I did not rolled down my card window, rather called up Bidhannagar traffic police and listed him the details of the incident.\n\nThis is to inform you as it concerns the on road security of any driving lady.\n\nRegards', '2018-04-19T15:22:53+0000', 'positive'),
