('129115403803409_1572648466116755', 'After 3 yrs came back to Kolkata.\nHave been following this FB page and got an impression that KP is not the KP we used to have 10-15 yrs back.\nSince I have been staying overseas for more than 11yrs and touching down to kolkata every 2-3 yrs i have witnessed that every time i come to this city there is something new happening around, but the traffic is still the same if not worse\nWhat changes have I noticed:\n1. People deliberately break the traffic rules Each time the red signal indicates 02 , 01 sec left to change to green the cars start honking their horns and starts moving even though the signal remaining red\n \n2 There are so many bilkes  and most of the people riding them don’t bother to follow any rules , and not only that people don’t bother to wear helmets and they don’t care .\n\n3 There seems to no lanes and even if there are few faint white lanes still visible but no one cares and 2 lanes become 5 lanes \n\nCurrently I am settled abroad so these features just tells me how day by day our traffic control is getting worse. \nIts so funny on one hand we are send satellites on the other hand  we are not able to provide and simple infrastructure.\nI think the KP should send experts abroad or invite experts from abroad to overhaul the whole traffic system which is just a mess\n\nI have photos and videos which can confirm my claims which i will upload on the social media to be viewed in the “funny videos”\n\nAlso i had an indirect encounter with a corrupt police who was threatening my driver Rs1000 for a minor infringement and then settled for Rs100 \nAnyways I am trying to get a video showing that corruption is still there in the police as it was in the past.', '2018-04-23T16:18:46+0000', 'negative'),
