('129115403803409_1573426242688264', 'Sir, \nKolkata traffic police had prosecuted my vehicle with Reg no WB20AG5096, for signal violation on 1st June, 2017. Case no: hhPC099555/17, Dated: 01-Jun-2017, Time: 19:47, Location:RASHBEHARI AVENUE/FERN ROAD. \nThe above case may have been prosecuted by mistake, though I was indeed on that above told location, but I am quite certain I haven\'t broke any stop line, or violated signal. Other than that, the timing of the case is also little off, because I had reached my destination Acropolis mall at 05:35 PM. The said place is about 3.5KM from incident place, which takes about 15 min in evening traffic. But the case was registered at 07:47PM. I have also attached my google location history of that day, hope that may support my claim.\nPreviously I contacted regurding above issue via message in this page. But as the issue was not updated in weekly visitors post, here I am posting it again. \nPlease let me know, if I did any wrong. I would be more than happy to pay for my mistake. \n\nThanks and regards \nSayantan Chowdhury', '2017-06-19T18:39:51+0000', 'positive'),
